\id REV  
\h Vatomwe 
\toc1 Jisas Krais le vatomwe weya Jon 
\toc2 Vatomwe 
\toc3 Vat 
\mt2 Jisas Krais Le  
\mt1 Vatomwe  
\mt2 Weya Jon  
\imt1 Utu iviva  
\ip Jon iye Jisas ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®, Sebedi nariye iyava i roriya bukuke iyake. Va i rori na i variye weŇčgiya ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® va inanji Eisiya provins e t…®ne. E mbaŇčako iyako Rom lenji mbaro i vur…®gheghe e yambaneke val…®vaŇčgako iyako, na th…® vakatha v…®r…® weŇčgiya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®. KiŇč…®ke iyava i vakatha v…®r…®ke weŇčgiya Kristiyan iye Sisa Nero. Iye va ghambaŇča mbaro theghathegha 54 i wa ve ghad theghathegha 68. KiŇč regha vambe i vakathava v…®r…® weŇčgiya Kristiyan, iye idae Domitiyan. Iye va ghambaŇča mboro theghathegha 81 ghaghad theghathegha 96. R…®ghe lagh…®ye vara na th…® vakatha v…®r…® weŇčgiya Kristiyan Ňčgoreiyake. Rom va th…®Ňča lenji kiŇč…®ko iye Ňčgoreiya loi regha na ghar…®ghar…® wo th…® kururuwe. Ko iyemaeŇčge Kristiyan thiye va th…® botewo na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKrais iye ghama Giya na mbe wo kururuwe eŇčge vara amalagh…®niye.‚ÄĚ Iyake kaiwae Rom lenji rambarombaro th…® th…®gh…®ya wanaŇčgiya Kristiyan na th…® gaboŇčgiya vavana (2:10; 2:13; 3:10; 6:9).  
\ip Rom vambe th…® vaŇčguraweva Jon e thiyo e raurau Pat…®mos t…®ne (1:9). Buk gharaghareghare lemoyo th…®Ňča KiŇč Domitiyan ghambaŇča e t…®ne, mbwata theghathegha 95 e t…®ne. MbaŇčaniye Jon vambe ina Pat…®mos e t…®ne Jisas i vatomweya bigibigi vavanawe na i uturaŇčgiya.  
\ip Jon i govambwara weŇčgiya Kristiyan Seitan le vakatha v…®r…® weŇčgiya ekelesiya ne i lagh…®ye, ko iyemaeŇčge thiye mbe th…® ndeghath…® vur…®gheghe vara othembe thoŇčgo th…® vaidiya mare (12:11). RenuwaŇča lagh…®ye regha mbe th…® ghataŇčaghath…® vara (2:7; 13:10; 14:12). Jon i govambwara Krais ne i njoghama amba i kivwalaŇčgiya ghath…®gh…®ya. Thavala ghanjithanavu i thar…® ne i lith…® weŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® ne th…® rakaru e yambane togha na buruburu togha e ghathovuye t…®ne (21:7-8).  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Bukuke iyake Jisas Krais le vatomwe utuniye. Loi va i giya bigibigike thiyakewe na i woraŇčgiya weinda ghinda le rakakaiwo budakaiya tene i yomara ma mbaŇča molao. Krais va i variya le nyao thovuye e ghino, Jon, wovatomwe e t…®ne na i vatomweya bigibigike thiyake weŇčgo.  
\v 2 Na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye ya thuweŇčgiko ya govambwara e ghemi. Loi ghal…®Ňčae na Jisas Krais le woraŇčgiya e ghino ya utuŇča utuniye e ghemi.  
\v 3 Thela thoŇčgo i vaona weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® utuutuke iya Loi ghal…®Ňčaeke totoke e ghabuku t…®ne, iye Loi i warari kaiwae, na thavala th…® loŇčweya utuutuke iyake na th…® ghambu, Loi i warari kaiwanji. Kaiwae ma mbaŇča molao kaero bigibigike thiyake th…® yomara.   
\s1 Jon i gomwaewo ekelesiya ghepir…® weŇčgi  
\p
\v 4 Ghino Jon, ya roriya letake iyake na ya variye i ghaona e ghemi ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® inami e val…®vaŇčga Eisiya t…®ne.  
\p Ya naŇčgo weya Loi iye noroke, mbaŇča me vivako, na mbaŇča i menamenake mbe inawe, ghare weŇčga na le gharemal…®l…® i riyevanjara gharemina. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva nyao theghepir…®\f + \fr 1:4 \ft Nyao theghepir…® mbwata th…® meth…® Nyao Boboma. Mbowo hu thuweva Vat 3:1.\f* thiya inanji Loi e ghamwae ele ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne, thiye th…® meth…® Nyao Boboma,  
\v 5 weiye Jisas Krais gharenji weŇčga na lenji gharemal…®l…® i riyevanjara gharemina. Jisas iye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharayathu emunjoru, iye mare ghagamau, na iye yambaneke ghakiŇč lenji randeviva.  
\p Jisas iye i gharethovuinda, le mare e t…®ne i rakayathuinda na i thavwiyathu la thar…®;  
\v 6 ko amba i bigiraweinda le ghamba mbaro ghar…®ghar…®niye. Ghinda ra tabo le rakakaiwo boboma le Loi na Ramae kaiwae. Jisas iye ra wovavwenyevwenye na ra wovavur…®vur…®ghegheŇča mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye, ma ele ghambako. Mbwana. Ňägoreiye.   
\pi1
\v 7 Wo hu thuwe! Iye iya i njama e Ňčgal…®l…®ko, ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye maranji ne i voro na th…® thuwe,  
\pi1 na othembe thavala va th…® vwe na i mare, thiye tembene th…® thuweva.  
\pi1 Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke ne th…® randa kaiwae.  
\pi1 Emunjoru! Mbwana. Ňägoreiye.   
\p
\v 8 Loi iye i Vur…®gheghe Moli, na iye noroke, mbaŇča me vivako, na mbaŇča i menamenake mbe inawe, iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Alepa na Omega, ghino va e R…®ghendake na ne Eleghambakoko.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jon i thuweya Jisas  
\p
\v 9 Ghino ghaghami Jon, weya Jisas weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi ra vaidiya v…®r…®, kaiwae weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi ra tabo Jisas le ghamba mbaro ghar…®ghar…®niye na weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi ra ghataŇčaghath…®gha vuyowo weinda la rouda. Va ya vavaghareŇča Loi ghal…®Ňčae na Jisas Krais le woraŇčgiya e ghino, na iyake kaiwae th…® yak…®n…®Ňčgo na th…® vaŇčguraweŇčgo e raurau Pat…®mos na va yakuwe.  
\v 10 Ghanda Giya ghambaŇča kururu e t…®ne, Nyao Boboma le vur…®gheghe i woŇčgo, amba ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®ye regha e ghereiŇčgu Ňčgoreiya mema ghal…®Ňčae.  
\v 11 IŇča Ňčgoreiyake, ‚ÄúBigibigike iya ne u thuweŇčgike u rorinjoŇča e peipa von…®vona t…®ne, ko ambane u variye na i wa weŇčgiya ekelesiya thiya yaku e ghembaghemba theghepir…® t…®nenji na th…® vaona. Ghembaghemba theghepir…® thiyake: Epesas, Smaina, Pegamam, Tayataira, Sadis, Piladelpiya na Leodisiya.‚ÄĚ\fig Ya thuweŇčgiya kad…®ŇčeŇče weinji ghambanji|alt="seven golden lampstands" src="bk00154b.tif" size="col" copy="BFBS (Knowles-Bass)" ref="1:12" \fig*   
\p
\v 12 Amba ya ndev…® na nuwaŇčguiya ya thuwe thela me utuutuko weŇčgo, iwaeŇčge ya thuweŇčgiya kad…®ŇčeŇče weinji ghambanji gol, lenji ghanaghanagha ghepir…®.  
\v 13 E ghanjilughawoghawo ya thuweya yamoyamo regha Ňčgoreiya lolo\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Dan 7:13\x* i njimbo kwama ghayaboyabo molao, i nja ve wo gheghe, na gharevwata gheva th…® vakatha gol i livagh…®liya.  
\v 14 Umbaliye vulivuliye i kakaleva Ňčgoreiya ghina ree, na maramarae Ňčgoreiya nd…®ghe mamiye.  
\v 15 Gheghe th…® ndalandala Ňčgoreiya th…® Ňčambwa kopa na th…® vakatha na i ndalandala, na ghal…®Ňčae ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiya mbwa i voru e thalawovanja laiye.  
\v 16 N…®mae e uneke i laweŇčgiya gh…®tara vogh…®pir…®, na gaith…® ghaghalith…® lawelaweniye marae vaŇčga na vaŇčga i raŇčgima e ghae. Ghamwae marambwelambwelawae Ňčgoreiya raŇčgila thiyo varaeniye.   
\p
\v 17 MbaŇča ya thuweya loloko iyako, ya dobu e gheghe Ňčgoreiya lolo kaero i mare. Kaero i liraweya n…®mae uneko e riwaŇčgu na iŇča, ‚ÄúTha u mararu! Ghino va e R…®ghendako na Eleghambakoko.  
\v 18 Ghino e yawayawaliŇčgu, va ya mare, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčake kaero e yawayawaliŇčgu na ya meghabana mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye. Mare na Thambe ghanjiki ghino ya mbaroŇča.  
\v 19 Bigibigike iya mo thuweke, na iya kaero nanjiwe e mbaŇčake iyake na iya ne th…® yomara mbaŇča i menamenako, u rorinjoŇča utuutuninji.  
\v 20 Simosimoko iya mo thuweŇčgiko ‚ÄĒ gh…®tara vogh…®pir…® me nanji e n…®maŇčguke e uneŇčguke na kad…®ŇčeŇče weinji ghambanji gol lenji ghanaghanagha theghepir…® ghanjirumwaru Ňčgoreiyake: gh…®tara vogh…®pir…® thiye nyao thovuthovuye ekelesiyama ghepir…®ma ghanjiranjimbunjimbu, na kad…®ŇčeŇče weinji ghambanji gol lenji ghanaghanagha ghepir…®, thiye ekelesiya ghepir…®ma.‚ÄĚ   
\c 2  
\s1 Toto ekelesiya Epesas kaiwanji  
\p
\v 1 Amba loloko iyako i dage weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya leta na i wa Epesas, i wa weya nyao thovuye iya ekelesiyako gharanjimbunjimbuma, na u utuwe Ňčgoreiyake:\fig |alt="Map of the Seven Churches of Asia" src="Seven ChurchesSUDU.tif" size="col" loc="Rev 2‚Äď3" copy="SIL" ref="Vat 2:1" \fig*  
\pi1 Loloma iya e n…®maeke uneke i laweŇčgiya gh…®tarama ghepir…®, na i loŇčgaloŇčga Ňčgoreiya kad…®ŇčeŇče weinji ghambanji gol lenji ghanaghanagha ghepir…® e t…®nenji ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake:  
\v 2 Ghamithanavu kaero ya ghareghare, lemi rovur…®gheghe e kaiwo na lemi ghataŇčaghath…® weiye lenji rouda. Kaero ya ghareghare hu th…®gh…®ya wanaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko raraithar…®. Th…®Ňčava thiye ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®, ko iyemaeŇčge ma Ňčgoreiye. Kaero hu tuthiya lenji utuutuko na hu vaidiŇčgi ko ana thiye rakwan.  
\v 3 Kaero ya ghareghare idaŇčgu kaiwae hu vaidiya v…®r…®, ko iyemaeŇčge hu ghataŇčaghath…® na ma hu njavovo.   
\pi1
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge ya vaidiya bigi regha ya wovathar…®thar…®Ňča e ghemi Ňčgoreiyake, mbaŇčake ma hu gharethovu wagiyawe Ňčgoreiya va i vivama.  
\v 5 Wo hu renuwaŇča lemi gharethovuko le lagh…®lagh…®ye va iyako, ambane hu ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga lemi dobu na le molamolao. Wo hu roiteteŇčgiya ghamithanavuna raraithar…® na ghamithanavu ne Ňčgoreiya va hu vakathakaiko. ThoŇčgo ma hu ndeghereiye wanaŇčgiya ghamithanavu raraithar…®, ne ya ghaona e ghemi na ya th…®na lemi kad…®ŇčeŇčena weiye ghambaena.  
\v 6 Ko iyemaeŇčge bigi regha ya warariŇča weŇčga, iyake ‚ÄĒ wabwi Nikolaita ghanjithanavu hu botewoyathu na ghino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ya botewoyathu.   
\pi1
\v 7 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, budakaiya Nyao Boboma i utuŇča ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® weŇčgi ne hu loŇčwe. Thavala th…® kivwalaŇčgiya thar…®, ne ya vatomwe weŇčgiya yawal…®ko ghaumbwa une na th…® ghan, iya i ndeghath…® Loi ele umako buruburu e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Toto ekelesiya Smaina kaiwanji  
\p
\v 8 Tembe i dageva weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya leta na i wa Smaina, i wa weya nyao thovuye iya ekelesiyako gharanjimbunjimbuma, na u utuwe Ňčgoreiyake:  
\pi1 Loloke iya iye va R…®ghendako na ne Eleghambakoko; iye vambowo i mare na kaerova i thuweiruva na e yawayawaliye, ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake:  
\v 9 Hu vaidiya v…®r…® na ma e lemi bigibigi kaero ya ghareghare, ko iyemaeŇčge Loi e marae ghemi hu vwenyevwenye. Kaero ya ghareghare Jiu vavana th…® utuvathar…® e ghemi. Thiye th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėMbe ghime eŇčge Loi le wabwi,‚Äô ko iyemaeŇčge ma Ňčgoreiye, ko ana thiye Seitan le wabwi ghar…®ghar…®niye.  
\v 10 Tha hu mararu the bigiya ne hu vaidiya vuyowae. Wo hu vandeŇčeŇčgo! Seitan ne iŇča amba th…® laweŇčga ghemi vavana na th…® bigiraweŇčga e thiyo na th…® mandowa lemi loŇčweghath…®na. Ne hu vaidiya v…®r…® lagh…®ye na mbaŇča theyaworo e t…®ne amba v…®r…®ko iyako iko. Ko iyemaeŇčge hu ndeghath…® vur…®gheghe e lemi loŇčweghath…®na, othembe ne hu vaidiya mareniye, ghino tene ya giya lemi ghataŇčaghath…®na modae yawal…® memeghabananiye.   
\pi1
\v 11 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, budakaiya Nyao Boboma i utuŇča ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® weŇčgi ne hu loŇčwe. Thavala th…® kivwalaŇčgiya thar…®, thiye mare theghewoniye v…®r…®niye mane nasiye mun regha th…® vaidi.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Toto ekelesiya Pegamam kaiwanji  
\p
\v 12 Tembe i dageva weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya leta na i wa Smaina, i wa weya nyao thovuye iya ekelesiyako gharanjimbunjimbuma, na u utuwe Ňčgoreiyake:  
\pi1 Loloko iya gaith…®ko ghaghalith…® marae vaŇčga na vaŇčga na lawelaweniye inawe ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake:  
\v 13 Ya ghareghare aŇčga inami hu yaku na ghembana iyana Seitan i mbaroŇča. Othembe Ňčgoreiyako mbe hu ndevadedeŇčgo vara. Lemi loŇčweghath…® e ghino ma hu roitete, othembe va th…® tagavamara lo rayathu thovuye Antipas e ghembana iyana t…®ne, na ghembana iyana Seitan le ghamba yaku inawe.   
\pi1
\v 14 Ko iyemaeŇčge bigibigi vavana ya wovathar…®thar…®Ňča e ghemi. E lemi wabwina t…®ne ghar…®ghar…® vavana inanjiwe th…® ghambugha Balaam le vavaghare. Iye va i vatomwe weya Balak na mbala i vabeŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® vakatha thar…®. Lenji thar…®ko vambe th…® ghana ghan…®Ňčga iya kaero th…® vowoŇča weŇčgiya loi vakavakatha na vambe th…® vakavakathava yathima thanavuniye raraithar…®.  
\v 15 Ghemi tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, e lemi wabwina t…®ne, ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® ghambugha wabwi Nikolaita lenji vavaghare.  
\v 16 Iya kaiwae wo hu roiteteŇčgiya lemi thar…®na na hu ndeghereiyewanaŇčgi. ThoŇčgo ma ma Ňčgoreiyako, mbaŇča nasiye ya ghaona e ghemi, na ya wo gaith…®ko ghaghalith…® me raŇčgima e ghaeŇčguke na ya gaith…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®na thiyena.   
\pi1
\v 17 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, budakaiya Nyao Boboma i utuŇča ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® weŇčgi ne hu loŇčwe. Thavala th…® kivwalaŇčgiya thar…®, ne ya giya ghan…®Ňčga manna th…® ghan, iya mbaŇčake amba i rothuweleko. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ne ya giya var…® kakaleva regha na regha weŇčgi, var…®ko iyako e riwae ya roriya ida toghawe, na idako iyako ma lolo regha ne i ghareghare, mbe thelaeŇčge vara ne i wo iye i ghareghare.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Toto ekelesiya Tayataira kaiwanji  
\p
\v 18 Tembe i dageva weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya leta na i wa Tayataira, i wa weya nyao thovuye iya ekelesiyako gharanjimbunjimbuma, na u utuwe Ňčgoreiyake:  
\pi1 Loi Nariye, iye marae Ňčgoreiya nd…®ghe mamiye na gheghe th…® ndalandala Ňčgoreiya th…® Ňčambwa kopa na th…® vakatha na i ndalandala, ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake:  
\v 19 Kaero ya ghareghare ghamithanavu, lemi gharethovu, lemi loŇčweghath…®, lemi kaiwo na lemi ghataŇčaghath…®. Ya ghareghare va i viva ghamithanavu i thovuye, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčake kaero i thovuye moli.   
\pi1
\v 20 Ko iyemaeŇčge bigi regha ya wovathar…®thar…®Ňča e ghemi, wevoke iyake, Jesabel. Elagh…®niye iŇčava Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, na hu vatomwe i yaku e ghemi. I vaghare vathar…®Ňčgiya lo rakakaiwo, iya kaiwae th…® vakavakatha yathima thanavuniye raraithar…®, na th…® ghana ghan…®Ňčga kaero th…® vowoŇča weŇčgiya loi vakavakatha.  
\v 21 Kaerova ya giya ghambaŇča na mbalava i ndeghereiyewana yathimako thanavuniye raraithar…®, ko iyemaeŇčge i botewoyathu.  
\v 22 Iya kaiwae ya lith…®we na ne i ghambwera na i ghataŇča v…®r…®. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thavala weiyaŇčgi th…® vakavakatha yathima thanavuniye raraithar…® na ma th…® ndeghereiyewana ghathanavuko iyako, ne th…® vaidiya vuyowae lagh…®ye moli.  
\v 23 Gharaghambu tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ne ya tagavavamareŇčgi, na mbala ekelesiyake wolagh…®ye th…® ghareghare ghino ya tuthiya ghar…®ghar…® gharenji na lenji renuwaŇča, ko amba ya giya regha na regha modami Ňčgoreiya budakaiya lemi vakatha.   
\pi1
\v 24 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghemi Tayataira, thavala ma hu goru weya le vavaghareko raithar…® iyako, na mava hu vakatha iya vavana th…®Ňčako, ‚ÄėSeitan le renuwaŇča thuwethuweleniye,‚Äô ya dage e ghemi ma tene ya giyava ghamivuyowo regha, mbema yaŇča eŇčge Ňčgoreiyake:  
\v 25 vavaghareko kaerova hu woko, hu njimbukiki wagiyawe ghaghad ya njoghama.   
\pi1
\v 26-27 Thavala th…® kivwalaŇčgiya thar…®, na th…® vakavakatha lo renuwaŇča i wa ghaghad mbaŇča ele ghambako, iya mbaroko le vur…®gheghe Bwebwe va i woveŇčgoko ne ya wogiya weŇčgi, na mbala thiye e lenji vur…®gheghe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye. Lenji mbaro ne i vur…®gheghe weŇčgi, na ne th…® vakowanaŇčgi Ňčgoreiya lolo i tagagh…®th…®gh…®tha uye.\x - \xo 2:26-27 \xt Sam 2:9\x*  
\v 28 Na tembene ya giya weŇčgiva gh…®tara th…®nambaŇča vogh…®t…®na.  
\v 29 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami budakaiya Nyao Boboma i utuŇča ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® weŇčgi ne hu loŇčwe.‚ÄĚ   
\c 3  
\s1 Toto ekelesiya Sadis kaiwanji  
\p
\v 1 Tembe i dageva weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya leta na i wa Sadis, i wa weya nyao thovuye iya ekelesiyako gharanjimbunjimbuma, na u utuwe Ňčgoreiyake:  
\pi1 Loloko iya i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya nyao theghepir…®, thiya th…® kaiwo Loi kaiwae, na iya n…®mae e uneke i laweŇčgiya gh…®tara vogh…®pir…®,\f + \fr 3:1 \ft Nyao theghepir…® mbwata th…® meth…® Nyao Boboma lagh…®ye. Mbowo hu thuweva Vat 3:1. Gh…®tara vogh…®pir…® th…® meth…® nyaoko thovuthovuye theghepir…® ekelesiyako theghepir…® ghanjiranjimbunjimbu.\f* ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake: Kaero ya ghareghare ghamithanavu. Ghamiyamoyamo Ňčgoreiye mbe e yawayawalimi, ko iyemaeŇčge kaero hu mare.  
\v 2 Thama ghanjighena! Hu rakathuweiru na hu vavur…®gheghe ghathanavu thovuye na thava i mare moli, kaiwae kaero ya vaidiŇčga ghamithanavu amba ma i thovuye lo Loi e marae.  
\v 3 Vavaghareko thovuye iyava hu loŇčweko na hu wovatha wo hu renuwaŇčakiki! Iya kaiwae hu ghambu na hu ndeghereiyewana ghamithanavu raraithar…®. Ko thoŇčgo mbe hu ghenaghena vara na ma hu thuweiru, ne ya ghaona e ghemi. Mane hu ghareghare thembaŇča ya ghaona, ne lo ghaona Ňčgoreiya rakaiv…® lenji vutha.  
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge Sadis ghar…®ghar…®niye vavanaeŇčge ghanjikwama ma i mbigh…®, ma th…® vakowanaŇčgi e thar…® thanavuniye. Nevole th…® njimbo kwama kakaleva na weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ya loŇčga na regha kaiwae thiye e ghanjithovuye.   
\pi1
\v 5 Thavala th…® kivwalaŇčgiya thar…®, ne th…® njimbo kwama kakaleva Ňčgoreiyako. Mane ya nderakayathumun idanji yawal…® e ghabuk t…®ne. Ko iyemaeŇčge Bwebwe weiyaŇčgiya le nyao thovuthovuye e maranji ne ya govambwaraŇčgi na yaŇča, ‚ÄėThiye lo ghar…®ghar…®.‚Äô   
\pi1
\v 6 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, budakaiya Nyao Boboma i utuŇča ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® weŇčgi ne hu loŇčwe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Toto ekelesiya Piladelpiya kaiwanji  
\p
\v 7 Tembe i dageva weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya leta na i wa Piladelpiya, i wa weya nyao thovuye iya ekelesiyako gharanjimbunjimbuma, na u utuwe Ňčgoreiyake:  
\pi1 Loloko iya i bobomako na i emunjoru, iya Deivid le ki inawe na mbaŇča ne i vugha th…®n…®mba ma tembe val…®kaiwaeva lolo regha i th…®n…®t…®mo, na mbaŇča ne i ki ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha tembe i vughava. Loloko ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake:  
\v 8 Kaero ya ghareghare ghamithanavu. Kaero ya vugha th…®n…®mba e ghamwami iya ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha i th…®n…®t…®mo. Ya ghareghare othembe lemi vur…®gheghe ma i lagh…®ye, kaero hu ghambugha lo vavaghare na ma hu roroya idaŇčgu.  
\v 9 Wo hu thuwe! Ne ya vakatha Seitan le wabwiko ghar…®ghar…®niye iya th…®Ňčakova thiye Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye ko nandere. Thiye th…® kwan. Ne ya vakatha na th…® mena th…® kururu e ghamwami na th…® govambwara ya gharethovuŇčga.  
\v 10 Kaiwae kaero hu ghambugha lo mbaro na hu ghataŇčaghath…® weiye lemi rouda, tembene ya njimbughath…®Ňčgava e vuyowoko wolagh…®ye t…®ne iya i menamenako e yambaneke na i mandoŇčgiya rameyambanewe.  
\v 11 MbaŇča nasiye ya ghaona e ghemi. Budakai kaerova hu wo hu vikiki wagiyawe na mbala ma lolo regha i wo e ghemi lemi ghataŇčaghath…®na modae.   
\pi1
\v 12 Thavala th…® kivwalaŇčgiya thar…® ne ya bigira weŇčgi na th…® tabo lo Loi le Ňägolo Boboma ghambagh…®mbagh…®, na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye mbene th…® yakuyaku vara gheko. Ne ya roriya lo Loi idae weŇčgi na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghambae idae, Jerusalem Togha iya ne i njama e buruburu weya amalagh…®niye. Na tembene ya roriva ghino idaŇčgu togha weŇčgi.  
\v 13 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, budakaiya Nyao Boboma i utuŇča ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® weŇčgi ne hu loŇčwe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Toto ekelesiya Leodisiya kaiwanji  
\p
\v 14 Tembe i dageva weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya leta na i wa Leodisiya, i wa weya nyao thovuye iya ekelesiyako gharanjimbunjimbuma, na u utuwe Ňčgoreiyake:  
\pi1 Totoke iyake i mena weya loloko iya th…®Ňčako iye ‚ÄėMbwana! Ňägoreiye!‚Äô, iye rayathu thovuye na emunjoru, na iye bigibigike wolagh…®ye Loi va i vakathaŇčgike r…®ghenji, ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake:  
\v 15 Kaero ya ghareghare ghamithanavu. Ya ghareghare ma hu njigh…®njigh…® na ma hu dayagha ghino kaiwaŇčgu. Ma hu botewoŇčgo, ko iyemaeŇčge ma Ňčgoreiya weimi lemi warari na hu ghambugha ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu. Ko ana nuwaŇčguiya hu njigh…®njigh…® o hu dayagha!  
\v 16 Ko iyemaeŇčge kaiwae mbe val…®vaŇčga eŇčge lemi gharevatomwe na lemi loŇčweghath…® e ghino ne ya njoŇčgoyathuŇčga.  
\v 17 Kaiwae huŇča, ‚ÄėGhime wo vwenyevwenye na bigibigike wolagh…®ye i thovuye weime, ma wo kwara e bigi regha.‚Äô Ko ana ma hu ghareghare nami e vuyowo lagh…®ye t…®ne na ghar…®ghar…® gharenji i v…®r…® kaiwami? Ghemi mbinyembinyeŇčgu, marami i kwaghe na hu bukabuka.  
\v 18 Iya kaiwae ya vavur…®ghegheŇčga, hu vamodo gol une moli e ghino, kaero th…® Ňčambu e nd…®ghe na i ndayathu murimuriye, amba ne hu vwenyevwenyewe. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva hu vamodova kwama kakaleva e ghino na hu njimbo na hu yabwa monjinamina na lemi monjinana iko. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva hu vamodo maramina ghaghethawari e ghino na hu liŇčgi e maramina amba ne val…®kaiwami hu thuwe.   
\pi1
\v 19 Thavala ya gharethovuŇčgi ya goviya ghamwanji na ya vathanavuŇčgi ghanjithanavu raraithar…® kaiwae. Iya kaiwae hu rovur…®gheghe thanavu thovuye kaiwae na hu ndeghereiyewana thanavu raithar…®.  
\v 20 Wo hu thuwe! Ya ndeghath…® e Ňčgolo ghath…®n…®mba na ya d…®gh…®d…®gh…®. ThoŇčgo thela i loŇčweya ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke na i vugha le th…®n…®mba e ghino, ne ya ruwe na weiŇčgu wo ghan…®Ňčga na regha.   
\pi1
\v 21 Thavala th…® kivwalaŇčgiya thar…®, ne ya vatomwe weŇčgi wo yaku na regha elo ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne na wo mbaro na regha, Ňčgoreiya ghino va ya kivwala thar…® na weiŇčgu RamaŇčgu wo yaku na regha ele ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne.  
\v 22 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, budakaiya Nyao Boboma i utuŇča ekelesiya wabwi ghepir…® weŇčgi ne hu loŇčwe.‚ÄĚ   
\c 4  
\s1 Jon i thuweya Loi ele ghamba yaku t…®ne  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča bigibigiko thiyako th…® yomara na e ghereiye, amba ya thuweya buruburu ghath…®n…®mba i mavu. Na tembe ya loŇčweva ghal…®ghal…®Ňčama ma loŇčwema, Ňčgoreiya mema ghal…®Ňčae iŇča, ‚ÄúU voroma gheke na ya vatomwe e ghen budakaiya wone th…® yomara iyake e ghereiye.‚ÄĚ  
\v 2 E mbaŇčako iyako Nyao le vur…®gheghe i mbaroŇčaŇčgo na ya thuweya ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye e buruburu, lolo regha i yakuwe.  
\v 3 Loloko iyako ghayamoyamo i ndalandala Ňčgoreiye var…® jaspa na var…® sosoro idae kaniliyan lenji ndalandala. E ghamba yakuko iyako ya thuweya bwawo ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya var…® emerold marambwelambwelawae i vagh…®liya.  
\v 4 I vagh…®liya ghamba yakuko iyako, ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye yeiwo na ghevar…® (24), na giyagiya theiwo na theghevar…® th…® yakuwe, th…® njimbo kwama kakaleva na umbalinji ghamatabwaya gol.  
\v 5 E ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko iyako t…®ne vivilema na mb…®ler…® laiye i menamenawe. E ghamba yakuko iyako ghamwae kad…®ŇčeŇče vwarapir…® th…® rarawe, na thiyako nyao theghepir…® th…® kaiwo weya Loi. (Nyao theghepir…® thiye Loi Une.)  
\v 6 Na bigi regha ina e ghamba yakuko iyako ghamwae, ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya njigh…®ko i vakatha galas Ňčgoreiye krisitol.  
\p Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thetheghan theghevar…® ya thuweŇčgi, maramaranji i riyevanjara riwanjiko lagh…®ye, e ghamwanji na e ghereinji, na ghamba yakuko iya i yakukowe th…® megh…®liŇča.  
\v 7 Thetheghan regha Ňčgoreiya laiyon, theghewoniye Ňčgoreiya burumwaka, theghetoniye ghamwae Ňčgoreiya lolo, na theghevar…®niye Ňčgoreiya malagh…® i yoyo.  
\v 8 Thetheghan…®ko theghevar…®ko regha na regha vinevineiye ghewona na riwanjiko lagh…®ye maramaranji i riyevanjara na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva vineinjiko raberabe. Ghararagh…®ye na gougou th…® wothuwothu na ma th…® towotowo, th…®Ňča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúGiya Loi Vur…®gheghe Moli,  
\q2 iye i boboma, i boboma, i boboma,  
\q1 iye va inawe mbaŇča mevivako,  
\q2 e mbaŇčake na mbaŇča i menamenako.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 9 MbaŇča thetheghan…®ko thiyako th…® giya wovavwenyevwenye, yavwatata na vata ago weya iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko t…®ne, iya yawaliyeko memeghabananiye,  
\v 10 amba giyagiyama theiwo na theghevar…®ma th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye e ghamwae na th…® kururuwe. Th…® bigiraweya umbalinji ghamatabwaya e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko ghamwae, iya loloko i yakuwe, na th…® wothuwothu th…®Ňča,   
\q1
\v 11 ‚ÄúGhama Giya! Lama Loi,  
\q1 val…®kaiwae wo wovavwenyevwenyeŇčge,  
\q1 wo yavwatatawanaŇčge na wo taraweŇčge len vur…®gheghena kaiwae,  
\q1 kaiwae u vakatha bigibigike wolagh…®ye na len renuwaŇča e t…®ne th…® yomara na mbe inanjiwe vara.‚ÄĚ   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya thuweya peipa von…®vo mbambara th…® von, na ina loloko iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko e n…®mae val…®vaŇčga uneko. Peipako iyako gharorori ina e t…®ne na e vwatae kaero th…® von na mbaŇčapir…® th…® monjeghath…®.  
\v 2 Na ya thuweya nyao thovuye vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha i utuutu na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye moli iŇča, ‚ÄúThela ele r…®ghe na val…®kaiwae i tabeyathu monjemonjeko na i tateya peipa von…®voko iyako?‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Ko iyemaeŇčge ma lolo regha ina e buruburu, o e yambaneke o yambaneke e raberabe val…®kaiwae i tateya peipa von…®voko na i thuweya t…®neko.  
\v 4 IwaeŇčge ya randa lagh…®ye moli kaiwae ma th…® vaidiya lolo regha ele r…®ghe na val…®kaiwae i tateya peipa von…®voko iyako o i thuweya t…®neko.  
\v 5 Amba giyagiyama regha i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúThava u randa! Wo u thuwe! Iye th…® uno laiyon…®ko iya i mena Juda e ghauuko t…®ne, na iye Deivid rumbuye, kaero i vur…®gheghe kivwalaŇčgiya ghath…®gh…®ya na iye val…®kaiwae i tabeyathu peipa von…®voko ghamonjemonje ghepir…® na i tate.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 Ya tagath…®na maraŇčgu na ya thuweya Sip Nariye i ndeghath…® e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko ghadidiye na thetheghan theghevar…® weinjiyaŇčgiya giyagiyama e t…®nenji. Sip…®ko Nariye ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya kaerova th…® tagavamare. Ghasokisoki umbopir…® na maramarae vogh…®pir…®. Maramaraeko iyako nyao theghepir…® th…® kaiwo weya Loi Une Ňčgoreiya nyao theghepir…® i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgi e yambaneke lagh…®ye.  
\v 7 Sip…®ma Nariya i wa ve th…®na peipa von…®voma weya loloma i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyema e n…®mae uneko.  
\v 8 MbaŇča i vakatha iyako, thegheghan…®ma ghevar…®ma na giyagiyama theiwo na theghevar…®ma th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye e ghamwae. Giyagiyako regha na regha th…® mban e n…®man…®manji ghemwadimwadiwo hap na gaeba th…® vakatha e gol, inisen…®s\f + \fr 5:8 \ft Inisen…®s iye umbwa thiye butiye thovuye na modanji lagh…®ye moli.\f* i riyevanjaraŇčgi na iyako Ňčgoreiya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko lenji naŇčgo.  
\v 9 Thetheghan…®ko na giyagiyako th…® wothuŇča wothu togha regha weya Sip…®ko Nariye th…®Ňča:  
\q1 ‚ÄúGhen e len r…®ghe na val…®kaiwan u th…®na peipa von…®voko iyako na u tabeyathu ghamonjemonjeko,  
\q1 kaiwae va th…® tagavamareŇčge,  
\q1 na mad…®bana e t…®ne ghar…®ghar…® uu na uu, ghal…®ghal…®Ňča na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča, ririwo na ririwo vanautuma na vanautuma u vamodonjoghaŇčgi Loi kaiwae.   
\q1
\v 10 Kaerova u vakathaŇčgi na len ghamba mbaro ghaghar…®ghar…® boboma na thiye ravowovowo th…® kaiwo weya la Loi  
\q1 na thiye nevole th…® mbaroŇča yambaneke.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Amba ya tagath…®na maraŇčgu na ya thuweŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye, mbunja alalamaŇčgo na ya loŇčweya ghal…®Ňčanji. Th…® ndegh…®liŇča ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko, thetheghan theghevar…®ma, na giyagiyama.  
\v 12 Th…® wothu na ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye th…®Ňča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúSip Nariye iyava th…® tagavamareko, iya e la r…®ghe na val…®kaiwae ra taraweŇča le mbaro, ghavwenyevwenye, le thimba, na le vur…®gheghe, iye ra yavwatatawana, ra wovavwenyevwenye na ra tarawe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Na ya loŇčweya bigibigike wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji e buruburu, e yambaneke, e thalaute, e njigh…®te, na wolagh…®yeko th…® wothuwothu th…®Ňča,  
\p ‚ÄúWeya loloko iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko t…®ne, na weya Sip…®ko Nariye, ra taraweŇčgi, ra yavwatata wanaŇčgi, ra wovavwenyevwenyeŇčgi na ra wovavur…®vur…®ghegheŇčgi, mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye, ma ele ghambako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Thetheghan theghevar…®ma th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwana. Ňägoreiye.‚ÄĚ Na giyagiyama th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye na th…® kururu weŇčgi.   
\c 6  
\s1 Peipa monjemonje  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya thuweya Sip Nariye i tabeya monjemonje ghepir…®ma regha, iya i vivama, na ya loŇčweya thetheghan theghevar…®ma regha i kula na ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiye mb…®ler…® iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena!‚ÄĚ  
\v 2 Ya gh…®mara ghaoko, na gheko ya thuweya hos kakaleva. Loloko i thakowe i wo mbwenara; i li umbaliye ghamatabwaya na i wa ve gaith…® kivwalaŇčgiya ghath…®gh…®ya.   
\p
\v 3 MbaŇča Sip Nariye i tabeya monjemonjema theghewoniye, ya loŇčweya thetheghan…®ma theghewoniye i kula iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena!‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Na hos regha mbowo i raŇčgimava, i sosoro moli. Loloko i thakowe va i giya vur…®gheghewe na i womena gaith…® e yambaneke na i vakatha ghar…®ghar…® th…® vetagatagavamareŇčgi e gaith…® lagh…®ye. Na Loi i wogiyawa gaith…® ghaghalith…® lagh…®ye regha.   
\p
\v 5 MbaŇča Sip Nariye i tabeya monjemonjema ghetoninji, ya loŇčweya thetheghan…®ma theghetoninji i kula iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena!‚ÄĚ E mbaŇčako iyako ya thuweya hos bwedibwedi umbwara. Loloko i thakowe i th…®na sikeli regha e n…®mae.  
\v 6 Ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i mena thetheghan theghevar…®ko e t…®nenji Ňčgoreiya loloma iŇča, ‚ÄúU rughiya wit…®na kilogrem regha, modae Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča regha ghakaiwo modae, na u rughiya bali ghavuyowo kilogrem thegheto, modae Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča regha ghakaiwo modae, ko iyemaeŇčge ne u ndevakowana oliv…®na bunamawae na waena.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 MbaŇča Sip Nariye i tabeya monjemonjema ghevar…®ninji, kaero ya loŇčweya thetheghan…®ma ghevar…®ninji ghal…®Ňčae iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena!‚ÄĚ  
\v 8 E mbaŇčako iyako ya thuweya hos regha ghayamoyamo i talayaŇča. Loloko va i thakowe idae Mare na i rereghamba e ghereiye Thambe. I giya vur…®gheghe weŇčgi na th…® gaboŇčgiya yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya wan kota (1/4). Ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® mare e gaith…®, vavana th…® mare bada kaiwae, vavana ghambwera lagh…®ye kaiwae, na vavana thetheghan rawowoidi th…® ghar…®Ňčgi na th…® mare.   
\p
\v 9 MbaŇča Sip Nariye i tabeya monjemonjema ghelimaninji, kaero ya thuweya ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® gaboŇčgiko unenji e ghamba vowoko raberabe. Va th…® gaboŇčgi kaiwae th…® loŇčweghath…® Loi ghal…®Ňčae na lenji govambwara weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.  
\v 10 Th…® kula na ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGiya Memevoroniye, ghen u boboma na u utuutu emunjoru, ŇčgoroŇčga mbaŇča le molamolao na ne u vanivaŇčaŇčgiya yambaneke na u lith…® weŇčgi kaiwae va th…® gaboime?‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 Kaero i giya weŇčgiya kwama ghayaboyabo molao na kakaleva, amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu towo mbaŇča ubotuva, ghaghad oghaghami na oloumi, lemi val…®rakakaiwo, thiye ne th…® gaboŇčgi Ňčgoranjiya ghemi na lenji ghanaghanaghana i mboromboro.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 MbaŇča Sip Nariye i tabeya monjemonjema ghewonaninji, kaero ya thuweya ragheragheghe lagh…®ye regha i yomara. Varaeko marae i momouwo Ňčgoreiya kwama marae i bwedi moli, manjalako marae i soro Ňčgoreiya madibe,  
\v 13 na gh…®tara th…® dobudobunjama e buruburuko na th…® uunja e yambaneke, Ňčgoreiya umbwa fig uneune th…® Ňčgwe moli th…® dobudobu e ndamwae mbaŇča ndewendewe vur…®gheghe i vandindi.  
\v 14 Buruburu i vonjogha Ňčgoreiya peipa von…®vo na ouou na raurauke wolagh…®ye th…® roiteta ghambanji.  
\v 15 Amba yambaneke ghakiŇč…®Ňčgi, rambarombaroŇčgi, ragagaith…® lenji randeviva, ravwenyevwenye, na thavala idanji i lagh…®ye, weinjiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko, thiye rakakaiwobwaga na thiye rakarakayathuŇčgi, th…® rakavo na vethiya kubaro e bwaudu na var…®var…® molamolao e t…®nenji.  
\v 16 Th…® kula weŇčgiya ouou na var…®var…®ko th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúHu dobuma e vwatame na hu garubuime, na mbala loloko iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne ma i thuweime, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Sip Nariye le ghatemuru thava i mena weime.  
\v 17 Hu gavoime kaiwae lenji lith…® weime ghambaŇča lagh…®ye kaero i vutha, ma val…®kaiwae lolo reghava ne e yawayawaliye kaiwae lenji ghatemuruko.‚ÄĚ   
\c 7  
\s1 Ghar…®ghar…® lenji ghanaghanagha 144,000 ne e ghanjinono  
\p
\v 1 Iyake e ghereiye ya thuweya nyao thovuthovuye theghevar…® th…® ndeghath…® e yambaneke ghadidiye ghevar…® na th…® laweghath…®gha yambaneke ghandewendewe ghevar…® na mbala ma val…®kaiwae i rowo e yambaneke, e njigh…® o e umbwaumbwako.  
\v 2 Na mbowo ya thuweva nyao thovuye regha i mena yavorowoko e boimako i wo Loi e yawayawaliye le mbaro ghanono. Amba i kula na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye i wa weŇčgiya nyao theghevar…®ma iya me giya vur…®gheghema weŇčgi na th…® vakowana yambaneke na njigh…®.  
\v 3 IŇča, ‚ÄúThava wo hu vakowanaŇčgiya yambaneke, o njigh…® o umbwaumbwa, wo hu roroghagha ghaghad ne wo woraweya la Loi le nono le rakakaiwo e ghamwanji.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Kaero ya loŇčweya thiye e ghanjinono e ghamwanji lenji ghanaghanagha wan handred potipo tausan (144,000), th…® mena Isirel ghauuko wolagh…®ye weŇčgi.   
\q1
\v 5 Twel…®va tausan (12,000) th…® mena Juda e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 12,000 th…® mena Rubin e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 12,000 th…® mena Gad e ghauu t…®ne,   
\q1
\v 6 12,000 th…® mena Asa e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 12,000 th…® mena Manase e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 12,000 th…® mena Nap…®talai e ghauu t…®ne,   
\q1
\v 7 12,000 th…® mena Simiyon e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 12,000 th…® mena Livai e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 12,000 th…® mena Aisake e ghauu t…®ne,   
\q1
\v 8 12,000 th…® mena Sebulon e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 12,000 th…® mena Josep e ghauu t…®ne,  
\q1 na 12,000 th…® mena Benjamin e ghauu t…®ne.   
\s1 Jon i thuweya wabwi lagh…®ye moli thiya ndeghath…® e buruburu  
\p
\v 9 Iyako e ghereiye ya tagath…®na maraŇčgu, kaero ya thuweya wabwi lagh…®ye moli na ma val…®kaiwae ra vaona. Th…® raka mena e vanautuma wolagh…®ye, uu wolagh…®ye, ririwo wolagh…®ye, na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča wolagh…®ye. Thiya ndeghath…® loloko iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko na Sip Nariye e ghamwanji, th…® njimbo kwama molamolao kakaleva, na th…® mbana umbwaumbwa varegha ndamwandamwa e n…®manji.  
\v 10 Th…® kula na ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVamoru i mena weya la Loi iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko t…®ne, weiye Sip Nariye weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Nyao thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye th…® ndevagh…®liya ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko na giyagiyama weinjiyaŇčgiya thetheghan…®ma ghevar…®. Nyaoko thovuthovuye th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko ghamwae, ghamwanji i nja e thelauko vwatae na th…® kururu weya Loi,  
\v 12 th…®Ňča,  
\pi1 ‚ÄúMbwana. Ňägoreiye! Ra tarawe la Loi, ra wovavwenyevwenye, raŇča iye i thimba, ra vata agowe, ra yavwatatawana, raŇča iye rambarombaro memevoroniye na ra taraweŇča le vur…®gheghe mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako. Mbwana. Ňägoreiye!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Amba giyagiyama regha i vaitoŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúThavala ghar…®ghar…®ke iya th…® njimbo kwamake molamolao kakaleva na aŇčga th…® mena?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Ya gonjoghawe yaŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, ma ya ghareghare, ghen eŇčge u ghareghare.‚ÄĚ  
\p I dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ke thiyake th…® raka mena e vuyowo lagh…®ye t…®ne. Kaerova th…® thavwiya ghanjikwamako molamolao Sip Nariye e mad…®bae na i kakaleva.  
\v 15 Iya kaiwae th…® ndeghath…® Loi ele ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye ghamwae, na gougou na ghararagh…®ye th…® kaiwowe ele Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne; na loloko iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko t…®ne, th…® yaku weinji na i garubuŇčgi.  
\v 16 Ma tene bada i ghar…®Ňčgiva, ma tene mbwa i ghar…®Ňčgiva, na ma tene varae dayaghawae mane i vakowaŇčaŇčgiva,  
\v 17 kaiwae Sip Nariye iye ina e lughawoghawoko e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko, ne i njimbukikiŇčgi Ňčgoreiya sip gharanjimbunjimbu i njimbukikiŇčgiya le sip, ne i viva weŇčgi veth…® muna mbwako iya i voruvalaŇčako na e yawayawaliyeko. Na Loi ne i thavwiyathu maralumunjiko wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\c 8  
\s1 Sip Nariye i raka monjemonje ghepir…®ninji  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Sip Nariye i tabeya monjemonje ghepir…®ninji, ma tembe bigi regha laiye e buruburu mbaŇča le molamolao Ňčgoreiya lughawoghawo vaŇčgothiye.  
\v 2 Amba ya thuweya nyaoko thovuthovuye theghepir…® th…® ndeghath…® Loi e ghamwaema, na th…® vilambwa mema, tembe vwarapir…®va.   
\p
\v 3 Nyao thovuye reghava, i th…®na gaeba th…® vakatha e gol na i mena i ndeghath…® e ghamba vowo ghadidiye. Inisen…®s lemoyo Loi i giyawe na i Ňčambu vatabo raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko wolagh…®ye lenji naŇčgo e ghamba vowo gol ina e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye ghamwae.  
\v 4 Amba inisen…®s munduwae i voro weiye raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko lenji naŇčgo, th…® mena weya nyaoma thovuye iya i ndeghath…® Loi ghamwaema.  
\v 5 Nyaoko thovuye i th…®na gaebako na i wa e ghamba vowoko, ve takombana vowoko Ňčiyawe, na weiye le vur…®gheghe i liŇčginjoŇča e yambane. Amba mb…®ler…®r…® laiye, vivilema na ragheragheghe th…® yomara.   
\s1 Nyao thovuthovuye theghevar…® lenji mema  
\p
\v 6 Amba nyao thovuthovuye theghepir…® th…® vivatha lenji mema vwarapir…® na th…® uwi.   
\p
\v 7 Kaero nyaoko thovuye regha i uwiya le mema na mbaŇčara bigibigike thiyake th…® yomara; uye Ňčgoreiye var…® na nd…®ghe i mbumbu weiye madibe, weiye le vur…®gheghe i liŇčginjoŇča e yambaneke. Yambaneke val…®vaŇčga regha Ňčgoreiya wan ted (1/3) i nda, umbwaumbwa tembe Ňčgoreiyeva na nanako wolagh…®ye th…® ndavao.   
\p
\v 8 Na nyao thovuye theghewoniye i uwiya le mema, amba bigi regha Ňčgoreiya ou lagh…®ye regha i rara ve dobu e njigh…®ko t…®ne.  
\p Njigh…® val…®vaŇčga regha Ňčgoreiye wan ted (1/3) i gharav…® na madibe,  
\v 9 thetheghan e njigh…®ko t…®ne lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiye wan ted (1/3) thiya mare, na waŇčga tembe wan ted…®va (1/3) i mukuwoŇčgi.   
\p
\v 10 Nyao theghetoniye i uwiya le mema, amba gh…®tara lagh…®ye regha i ra Ňčgoreiye theŇčgi i rara i dobunjama e buruburuko, i unja e walawalagh…®ta Ňčgoreiye wan ted (1/3) na mbwarowou weŇčgi.  
\v 11 Gh…®tarako iyako idae maŇčgamaŇčga. Mbwako wolagh…®ye val…®vaŇčga le ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiye wan ted (1/3) th…® maŇčga, na ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo th…® muna maŇčgamaŇčgako na th…® mare.   
\p
\v 12 Amba nyao theghevar…®ninji i uwiya le mema. Varae, manjala na gh…®tara bigi regha i vakowanaŇčgi na mbala ma th…® mb…®le mbaŇča val…®vaŇčga le lagh…®lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiye wan ted (1/3). Mava varae i mb…®le val…®vaŇčga le lagh…®lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiye wan ted (1/3) ghararagh…®ye, na manjala na gh…®tara ma th…® mb…®le Ňčgoreiye wan ted (1/3) gougou.   
\p
\v 13 Amba ya tagath…®na maraŇčgu, na ya thuweya malagh…® i yoyo e lughawoghawoko na ya loŇčweya ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye, iŇča, ‚ÄúAleu, o thar…®! Aleu, o thar…®! Thar…® ne th…® yomara weŇčgiya rameyambane, mbaŇča ne nyaoko thovuthovuye theghetoko th…® uwiya lenji memako. Maiyavarake!‚ÄĚ   
\c 9  
\s1 Nyao thovuye theghelimaninji i uwiya le mema  
\p
\v 1 Amba nyao thovuye theghelimaninjima i uwiya le mema, na ya thuweya gh…®tarama iya me dobuma e buruburuko na i unja e yambaneke. Na i th…®n giyawa ki, goga iya i ghenenja moli ghaki.  
\v 2 MbaŇča gh…®tarama i vugha gogako umbaliye, mundu lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya nd…®ghe lagh…®ye munduwae i raŇčgima e t…®neko. Gogako iya i ghenenja moli iyako munduwae i poku lagh…®ye moli na i rogana varaeko marae mbouye.  
\v 3 Kaero bibita th…® raka raŇčgima e munduko t…®ne th…® rakanja e yambaneke, Loi i giya vur…®gheghe weŇčgi Ňčgoreiya theghegh…®yama e yambaneke lenji vur…®gheghe.  
\v 4 Va i dageten weŇčgi na thava th…® vakowana nana, o umbwa, o bigi i mbuthumbuthu, mbe iyaeŇčge vara ghar…®ghar…® ma Loi le nono na e ghamwanji th…® vakowanaŇčgi.  
\v 5 Loi mava i vatomwe weŇčgi na th…® r…®r…®vavamareŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge mbe th…® vakathaeŇčge v…®r…® weŇčgi mbaŇča le molamolao Ňčgoreiya manjala umbolima. Lenji vakathako Ňčgoreiya thethegh…®yama i vod…®gha lolo na le v…®r…®v…®r…®.  
\v 6 E mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako t…®nenji ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako ne v…®r…®ko kaiwae na th…® tamwetamweya mare, ko iyemaeŇčge othembe ne nuwanjiko nuwaiya th…® mare, mare ne i voiteteŇčgi.   
\p
\v 7 Bibitako thiyako Ňčgoranjiya hos kaero th…® vivathaŇčgi gaith…® kaiwae. E umbalinji bigi regha Ňčgoreiya umbalinji ghamatabwaya th…® vakatha gol na th…® bigirawe e umbalinji, ghamwanji ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya ghar…®ghar…® ghamwaghamwanji.  
\v 8 Umbalinji vulivuliye Ňčgoreiya wanakau umbalinji vulivuliye na ŇčiŇčinji Ňčgoreiya laiyon ŇčiŇčiye.  
\v 9 Gharenji vwatae e kunakunauye Ňčgoreiya gharenji vwatae ghaghetagagana th…® vakatha e aiyan, na vineinji laiye Ňčgoreiya hos th…® rukuliya sariyot lemoyo gaith…® kaiwae.  
\v 10 Wolounji Ňčgoreiya thethegh…®ya na mbe th…® vovod…®weva, e wolounjiko th…® vod…®Ňčgiya ghar…®ghar…®we le vur…®gheghe i vakatha v…®r…® iya i wo manjala umbolima.  
\v 11 E lenji kiŇč, i mbaroŇčaŇčgi. Iye gogama iya i ghenenja molima ghanyao raithar…®. Idae vaŇča Hibru th…®Ňča Abadon, na vaŇča Grik th…®Ňča Apoliyon.\f + \fr 9:11 \ft Abadon na Apoliyon ghanjirumwaru Ramukuwo.\f*   
\p
\v 12 Thar…® iviva kaero iko; thar…® theghewo amba iya th…® menamenako.   
\s1 Nyao thovuye theghewonaninji i uwiya le mema  
\p
\v 13 Amba nyao thovuye ghewonaninji i uwiya le mema, kaero ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i mena e ghamba vowo gol mbothiye ghevar…® weŇčgi, iya i yaku Loi e ghamwaeko.  
\v 14 I dage weya nyaoko thovuye iya ghewonaninjiko ele memako iŇča, ‚ÄúU rakayathuŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye theghevar…®, iya th…® Ňčgar…®Ňčgina na thiya yaku e Walagh…®ta Yupreitis.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 Kaero i rakayathuŇčgiya nyaoma thovuthovuye theghevar…® na veth…® tagavamareŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e yambaneke lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya wan ted (1/3). Loi va i laweghath…®Ňčgi ghaghad lughawoghawoke iyake, mbaŇčake iyake, manjalake iyake na theghatheghake iyake.  
\v 16 Lenji ragagaith…® th…® rakatha e hos vwatae, meth…® giya yanawaŇčgu lenji ghanaghanagha i wo tu handred miliyon.  
\v 17 E wovatomweko t…®ne ya thuweya hos na gharathatha ghanjiyamoyamo Ňčgoreiyake: Gharenji vwatae e ghaghetagagana, ghanjiyamoyamo th…® soro Ňčgoreiye nd…®ghe mamiye, th…® blu Ňčgoreiye var…® idae sapaya na th…® mbwaumbwau Ňčgoreiya salp. Hos…®ko umbalinji ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya laiyon umbalinji, na nd…®ghe, mundu na var…® salp i rara i raŇčgima e ghaenji.  
\v 18 Th…®vathar…® i mena e nd…®ghe, mundu na var…® salpa th…® raŇčgima hos…®ko e ghaenji; iya theghetoke iyake th…® gaboŇčgiya yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye val…®vaŇčga Ňčgoreiya wan ted (1/3) na thiya mare.  
\v 19 Hos…®ko lenji vur…®gheghe i mena e ghaenji na e wolounji. Kaiwae wolounjiko Ňčgoreiya mwata e umbaumbalinji na iyake th…® giya v…®r…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.   
\p
\v 20 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® iya thar…®ko theghetoko iyako mava i gaboŇčgi na thiya mare, mava th…® goru weya iyako, bigibigi vatavatad…®Ňčgi ma th…® ndeghereiye wanaŇčgi. Mbe th…® kurukururu weŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® na bigibigi vatavatad…®Ňčgi e gol, silva, kopa, var…® na umbwa. Bigibigiko thiyako ma val…®kaiwanji th…® thuwe, ma val…®kaiwanji th…® loŇčwe, ma val…®kaiwanji th…® loŇčga.  
\v 21 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako lenji gabo, lenji kukura na r…®mb…®re, lenji yathima thanavuniye, na lenji kaiv…® ma th…® ndeghereiye wanaŇčgi.   
\c 10  
\s1 Nyao thovuye i th…®na peipa von…®vo nasiye regha  
\p
\v 1 Na mbowo ya thuweva nyao thovuye vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha i njamanjama e buruburu. Ňägal…®l…® i ghavo vagh…®liya riwae Ňčgoreiya kwama molao, bwawo i thowo e umbaliye, ghamwae marambwelambwelawae Ňčgoreiye varae; na gheghe ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya tu th…® rara.  
\v 2 I th…®na peipa nasiye von…®vo mbambara kaero i taterawe. Gheghe e uneke ve vur…®ghath…®gha njigh…® na val…®vaŇčga e moiyeke ve vur…®ghath…®gha vanat…®na,  
\v 3 kaero i kula na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiya laiyon ghal…®Ňčae lavururuwae. MbaŇča i kula na e ghereiye mb…®ler…® ghepir…® th…® thombe e ghal…®Ňčanji.  
\v 4 MbaŇča mb…®ler…®ko th…® utuutu, na ghino ya munje ya roriya ghal…®Ňčanjiko, ko iyemaeŇčge ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i njama e buruburu iŇča, ‚ÄúBudakaiya mb…®ler…®ko ghepir…® meth…® utuŇča thava u utuŇča, thava u rorinjoŇča e buk.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Amba nyaoma thovuye iya ma thuweya me liraweya gheghe e njigh…® na vanat…®na, i li vaira n…®mae uneko na i vatomweya buruburu,  
\v 6 na i tholo loloko iya memeghabananiyeko e idae, iye va i vakatha buruburu na bigibiginiyeko wolagh…®ye, yambaneke na bigibiginiyeke wolagh…®ye, na njigh…® na bigibiginiyeko wolagh…®ye. I tholoko na iŇča, ‚ÄúRoroghagha ghambaŇča kaero iko!  
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčaniye nyao thovuye ghepir…®ninjima ne i uwiya le mema, Loi i vakathavuna le renuwaŇča memethuweleniye, Ňčgoreiya va i woraŇčgiya weŇčgiya le rakakaiwo ghal…®Ňčae gharautu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Amba ghal…®ghal…®Ňčama iya ma loŇčwema i mena e buruburu mbowo i dageva e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa, vo th…®na peipa von…®voma, kaero i matate na ina nyaoma thovuye iya i liraweya gheghema e njigh…®ko na vanat…®na e n…®mae.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Kaero ya wa weya nyaoma thovuye na va dagewe i th…®n…®giya peipa von…®voma nasiye e ghino. I dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúU th…®n na u ghan, e Ňčgamoina ne i maŇčge, ko iyemaeŇčge e ghaena ne gham…®nae Ňčgoreiyeva Ňčguyoma.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 Kaero ya th…®na peipa von…®voma nasiye nyaoma thovuye e n…®mae na ya ghan. E ghaeŇčguke i loghe Ňčgoreiya Ňčguyo, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča ya kovululu na venja e ŇčgamoiŇčgu gham…®nae i maŇčge.   
\p
\v 11 Amba i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa mbowo vo utuŇčava totoke iya Loi ghal…®Ňčaeke ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo kaiwanji, ghar…®ghar…® tomethi, vanautuma tomethi na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča tomethi kaiwanji, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva kiŇč lemoyo kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ   
\c 11  
\s1 Loi le ragogovambwara theghewo  
\p
\v 1 Amba nyao thovuye regha i wogiya umbwa regha e ghino Ňčgoreiya gherughirughima na i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa na vo rughiya Loi le Ňägolo Boboma na ghamba vowo, na thavala th…® kurukururu gheko tembe u wova lenji ghanaghanagha.  
\v 2 Ko iyemaeŇčge bakubakuna iya e Ňägolo Bobomana ghayayao t…®ne thava u rughi, kaiwae kaerova i wogiya weŇčgiya thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye na ne th…® vur…®njoŇčanjoŇča ghemba bobomako iyako mbaŇča le molamolao manjala ghwevar…® na umboiwo.  
\v 3 Ne ya variya lo ragogovambwara theghewo, ne th…® njimbo kwama iya i vatomwe th…® nuwathar…® thar…® kaiwae Ňčgoreiye, na th…® utuŇča iya Loi ghal…®Ňčae totoke. Ne th…® utu vworeŇča mbaŇča le ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya wan tausan tu handred sikisti (1,260).‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Ragogovambwarake iya theghewoke th…® ndeghath…® yambaneke gha Giya e ghamwae. Thiye Ňčgoranjiya oliv…®ma umboiwo na kad…®ŇčeŇčema vwaraiwo weinji ghambanji.  
\v 5 ThoŇčgo lolo regha i mando na i vakowanaŇčgi, nd…®ghe ne i raŇčgi e ghaenji na i ŇčambuvaoŇčgiya ghanjith…®gh…®ya. Thela nuwaiya i mando na i vakowanaŇčgi, le mare ne Ňčgoreiyako.  
\v 6 E lenji vur…®gheghe na val…®kaiwanji th…® kiya buruburuko na thava uye i nja ghanjimbaŇča yathuko e t…®ne. Tembe e lenji vur…®ghegheva na val…®kaiwanji th…® v…®va mbwa i tabo madibe. Na tembe val…®kaiwanjiva th…®Ňča na dagabora tomethi th…® yoyomara e yambaneke Ňčgoreiya lenji renuwaŇčako.   
\p
\v 7 MbaŇča ne th…® yathuvao totoko, thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko iya i voroma e gogama iya i ghenenja moli t…®ne ne i gaith…® weŇčgi. Ne i kivwalaŇčgi na i tagavavamareŇčgi,  
\v 8 na riwanjiko i yaku e ghemba idae lagh…®ye e ghakamwath…® mara. Ghembako iyako ghaida unouno th…®Ňča Sodoma na Ijipt, na e ghembako iyako t…®ne va th…® rokros ragogovambwara theghewoma ghanji Giyawe.  
\v 9 MbaŇča thegheto na vaŇčgothiye e t…®ne ghar…®ghar…® th…® raka mena e ririwo na ririwo, wabwi na wabwi, ghal…®ghal…®Ňča na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča, na vanautuma na vanautuma na th…® thuweya riwanjiko na mane th…® vatomwe na th…® bekuŇčgi.  
\v 10 Yambaneke gharayakuyaku nuwanji ne i loghe ragogovambwarake theghewoke lenji mare kaiwae. Ne th…® vakatha vawarari, th…® vegiya bigibigi weŇčgi weinjiyaŇčgiya ghanjiune, kaiwae ghal…®Ňčae gharautu theghewoke thiyake va th…® vakavakatha v…®r…® lagh…®ye weŇčgiya yambaneke gharayakuyaku.   
\p
\v 11 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča thegheto na vaŇčgothiye e ghereiye, amba Loi kaero i valawe yawal…® weŇčgi na e yawayawalinji amba th…® ndeghath…®. Ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® thuweŇčgiko th…® mararu lagh…®ye moli.  
\v 12 Amba ragogovambwarama theghewo th…® loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®ye regha i njama e buruburu iŇča, ‚ÄúHu voroma gheke.‚ÄĚ Ghanjith…®gh…®yama th…® ghewoŇčgi kaero th…® voro e buruburu e Ňčgal…®l…®ko.   
\p
\v 13 E lughawoghawoko iyako ragheragheghe lagh…®ye regha i yomara, na ghembako iyako val…®vaŇčga Ňčgoreiya wan ten…®t (1/10) na ŇčgoloŇčgoloniye thiya dobu bode. Ghar…®ghar…® lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya saven tausan (7,000) thiya mare ragheragheghe kaiwae, na thavala ma th…® mare weinji lenji mararu lagh…®ye na th…® tarawe buruburu gha Loi le vur…®gheghe.   
\p
\v 14 Vuyowo theghewoniye kaero iko, ko iyemaeŇčge vuyowo theghetoniye mbaŇča nasiye kaero i menava.   
\s1 Nyao theghepir…®ninji i uwiya le mema  
\p
\v 15 Amba nyaoma thovuye theghepir…®ninji i uwiya le mema, kaero ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® njama e buruburu th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúYambaneke ghambaro kaero ina vara Loi iye ghanda Giya na le Mesaiya e n…®manji ghare, na Loi iye rambarombaro mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye, ma ele ghambako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Amba giyagiyama theiwo na theghevar…®ma, iya thiya yaku e lenji ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyema Loi e marae, th…® ronja e gheghenji vuvuye na ghamwanji i t…®va e thelauko vwatae, th…® kururu weya Loi,  
\v 17 th…®Ňča:  
\q1 ‚ÄúGiya Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye,  
\q2 ghen inan…®we mbaŇčake iyake na mbaŇčako va i vivako e t…®nenji,  
\q1 wo vata ago e ghen  
\q2 kaiwae kaero u wo len vur…®gheghe  
\q2 na u tabo yambaneke gharambarombaro.   
\q1
\v 18 Thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® ghatemuru lagh…®ye e ghen,  
\q2 ko iyemaeŇčge len gaith…® lagh…®ye ghambaŇča kaero i mena.  
\q1 MbaŇča kaero i vutha na u vanivaŇčaŇčgiya thavala kaerova thiya mare.  
\q1 MbaŇča kaero i vuthava na len rakakaiwo ghal…®Ňčan gharautu u vamodaŇčgi,  
\q1 na raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko wolagh…®ye thiya th…® yavwatatawanaŇčge,  
\q1 thoŇčgo idaidanji lagh…®ye o thoŇčgo idaidanji nasiye,  
\q2 ne u giya modanji.  
\q1 MbaŇča kaero i mena na u mukuwoŇčgiya wolagh…®yeko va th…® gaboŇčgiya yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 19 Kaero Loi le Ňägolo Boboma e buruburu i mavu, na ya thuweya Dagerawe gha Bogis ele Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne. Amba vivilema, mb…®ler…® laiye, ragheragheghe na uye Ňčgoreiye var…®\f + \fr 11:19 \ft ‚ÄúUye Ňčgoreiye var…®‚ÄĚ gharumwaru uye va i tabona vur…®gheghe Ňčgoreiye vaŇča lumo raŇča ‚Äúice‚ÄĚ.\f* i yomara.   
\c 12  
\s1 Wevo na mwata lagh…®ye utuninji  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya thuweya nono lagh…®ye regha e buruburuko, na ghayamoyamoko mbe regha. Ya thuweya wevo eunda, ghakwama Ňčgoreiya varaeko, manjalako ina e gheghe raberabe na umbaliye ghamatabwaya weiye gh…®tara vogh…®yaworo na vogh…®wo ina e umbaliye.  
\v 2 I marabo, na i yawayawaru kaiwae Ňčgama kaero i vwara ghatambwa.   
\p
\v 3 Na i njana mbowo ya thuweva nono lagh…®ye regha e buruburuko, na ghayamoyamoko mbe regha. Na gheko ya thuweya mwata lagh…®ye regha sosoro. Umbaliye le ghanaghanagha ghepir…® na ghasokisoki le ghanaghanagha yaworo, na umbaliye regha na regha mbe e ghamatabwaya.  
\v 4 E wolouyeko i wanjiyathu gh…®tara val…®vaŇčga e buruburuko, le ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya wan ted (1/3), na th…® dobudobu th…® uunja e yambaneke. Kaero i wa ve ndeghath…® wevoma iya ghambaŇča ghamb…®ma e ghamwae na i roroghagha mbaŇča ne i ghamb…® kaero i ghana nariyeko.  
\v 5 Wevoma i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, iye weiye le vur…®gheghe wolagh…®ye ne i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya vanautumake wolagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge nyao thovuye i yowo Ňčgamako iyako e buruburu weya Loi na le ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne.  
\v 6 Wevoko i vo weya e njamnjam, e val…®vaŇčga regha Loi vama i vivatharawe kaiwae, na th…® njimbukiki mbaŇča le ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya wan tausan tu handred sikisti (1,260).   
\s1 Gaith…® i yomara buruburu  
\p
\v 7 Amba gaith…® i yomara e buruburu. Maikol weiyaŇčgiya le nyao thovuthovuye th…® gaith…® weinji mwata, na mwata weiyaŇčgiya le nyao th…® gaith…® njogha.  
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge Maikol na le wabwi th…® kivwalaŇčgiya mwatako na le wabwi, na ma th…® vatomweŇčgi na th…® yaku e buruburu.  
\v 9 Kaero th…® takoyathuŇčgiya mwatama lagh…®ye weiyaŇčgiya le nyaoma na th…® nja e yambaneke. Iye vambe i vivako mwataniye, idae th…®Ňča Devil o Seitan, na iye yambaneke lagh…®ye ghar…®ghar…®niye nuwanji gharavabe.  
\v 10 Amba ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®ye regha e buruburu iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake Loi weiye le vur…®gheghe kaero i vamoruŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®, iye KiŇč! MbaŇčake kaero i woraŇčgiya weinda le Mesaiya le mbaro ghavur…®gheghe! Kaiwae oghaghanda ghanjirawowonjowema, iye ghararagh…®ye na gougou i wonjoweŇčgi la Loi e marae, kaero th…® wokiyathu e buruburu.  
\v 11 Oghaghanda lenji vur…®gheghe va i mena Sip Nariye e mad…®bae, na kaiwae th…® gharevatomwe yawalinji yathu toto thovuye kaiwae, mava th…® mararuŇča mare, na iyako e t…®ne kaero th…® kivwala ghanjith…®gh…®ya Seitan.  
\v 12 Rameburuburu taulagh…®na ghemi wo hu warari! Ko iyemaeŇčge ghemi rameyambane na ghemi inami e njigh…®na t…®ne, o ma vuyowo i ghao e ghemi! Kaiwae Seitan kaero i njao e ghemi! Iye i gharegaith…® lagh…®ye moli kaiwae kaero i ghareghare ghambaŇča i tubo moli na val…®kaiwae i vakowaŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 MbaŇča mwatama i ghareghare kaero meth…® duyathu e yambaneke, amba i vagega wevoma iya va i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moruma.  
\v 14 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® giya malagh…®ma lagh…®ye vinevineiye weya wevoma, amba i yo na i wa e ghamba yakuko iya Loi va i vivatharaweko kaiwae, e njamnjam na i bwagabwaga weya mwatako. Na th…® njimbukiki gheko mbaŇča le molamolao Ňčgoreiya theghathegha umboto na vaŇčgothiye.  
\v 15 Amba mwatama i buturaŇčgiya mbwa e ghae Ňčgoreiya walagh…®tama i voru na i munjeva ŇčgonuŇčgo mbala i wo wevoma.  
\v 16 Ko iyemaeŇčge thelauko i thalavugha wevoko, i tateya ghae, na mbwa iya mwatama me butuyathu, i liŇčgimun.  
\v 17 Mwatama ghare i gaith…® lagh…®ye weya wevoma, kaero i wa ve vakatha gaith…® weiyaŇčgiya wevoko orumburumbuyeko wolagh…®ye, iya thavala th…® ghambugha Loi le mbaro na Jisas le vavaghare.   
\p
\v 18 Mwatama kaero i wa na ve ndeghath…® e njigh…®ko ghadidiye.   
\c 13  
\s1 Thetheghan mbwanjam na tagaith…® regha  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya thuweya thetheghan mbwanjam na tagaith…® regha i mun…®voroma e njigh…®ko t…®ne. Ghasokisoki hoyaworo na umbaliye le ghanaghanagha ghepir…®. E ghasoki regha na regha mbe e ghamatabwaya, na e umbaliye regha na regha th…® roriya ida reghawe, na idako iyako i govwaravwara Loi ghamwae.  
\v 2 Thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko iya ma thuweko ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya thetheghan lepad, gheghe Ňčgoreiya thetheghan beya\f + \fr 13:2 \ft Beya iya thetheghan lagh…®ye moli regha. Iye i yaku e ouou vwatavwatanji na e umbwaumbwa yambaneke val…®vaŇčga. Beya thiye tagaith…®Ňčgi na val…®kaiwae i gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.\f* gheghe, na ghae Ňčgoreiya laiyon ghae. Kaero mwatako i wogiya le mbaroko ghavur…®gheghe weya thetheghan mbwanjam na tagaith…®kowe, na thetheghan…®ko i yaku ele ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye na i tabo kiŇč.  
\v 3 Thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko umbaliye regha bola inawe, ghayamoyamo va th…® govamare, ko iyemaeŇčge ghaghalith…®ko marae tevambe i moi. I wo ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke vwata nuwanji na th…® ghambugha thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko iyako.  
\v 4 Ghar…®ghar…® th…® kururu weya mwatako kaiwae i giya le mbaroko ghavur…®gheghe weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, th…® kururu weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThela Ňčgoreiya thetheghan…®ke iyake? Thela ne val…®kaiwae i kivwala?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Loi i vatomweya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko na iye i wovorevoreŇča ghamberegha na i utuvathar…® weya Loi. Na Loi i wogiyawe na i mbaro manjala ghwevar…® na umboiwo.  
\v 6 I tateya ghae na i utuvathar…® weya Loi. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Loi idae, le ghamba yaku na rameburuburu i utuvathar…® weŇčgi.  
\v 7 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, Loi i vatomwe na i gaith…® weŇčgiya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko na i kivwalaŇčgi, na tembe i vatomwe weva na i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye; uu na uu, ririwo na ririwo, ghal…®ghal…®Ňča na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča na vanautuma na vanautuma.  
\v 8 Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke th…® kururuwe, ko iyemaeŇčge thavala Loi va i roriya idanji yawal…® e ghabuk t…®ne amba muyai i vakatha yambaneke, thiye mane th…® kururu weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko. Bukuko iyako Sip Nariye iyava th…® tagavamarema le buk.   
\p
\v 9 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, wo hu vandeŇče.  
\v 10 ThoŇčgo Loi i vatomweya lolo regha na th…® Ňčgar…®, ne th…® Ňčgar…®. ThoŇčgo i vatomweya lolo regha na th…® un…®gh…® e gaith…® ghaghalith…®, ne th…® un…®gh…® e gaith…® ghaghalith…®. Iyake kaiwae raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko weinji lenji loŇčweghath…® wo th…® ghataŇčaghath…®.   
\p
\v 11 Na i njana mbowo ya thuweva thetheghan mbwanjam regha i voroma e thelauko t…®ne. Ghasokisoki umboiwo Ňčgoreiya sip nariye ghasokisoki, na i utu Ňčgoreiya mwata i utu.  
\v 12 Thetheghan…®ma me vivako le mbaro ghavur…®ghegheko wolagh…®ye i valawe, na th…® yaku na regha weiye. Amba i vavur…®ghegheŇčgiya yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye wolagh…®ye na th…® kururu weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma me vivama, iya vambowo i marema, ko iyemaeŇčge gaith…® ghaghalith…® mara tevambe i moiva.  
\v 13 I vakathaŇčgiya vakatha vavana ghamba numowo, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghar…®ghar…® e maranji iŇča na nd…®ghe i ri e buruburu na i njama e yambaneke.  
\v 14 Loi i vatomwewe na i vakatha vakatha vavana thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma i vivama e ghamwae, na e t…®ne i wo ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke nuwanji na i yaroŇčgi. Amba i dage weŇčgi th…® vakatha thetheghan mbwanjam i vivama, iya vambowo th…® govamare e gaith…®ma ghaghalith…®, na mbaŇčake kaero e yawayawaliye, th…® monja ŇčgaliŇčgaliya na th…® vamidi ghayavwatata kaiwae.  
\v 15 I vatomwe thetheghan mbwanjam theghewoniyema i livalawe ghandewendewe weya thetheghan mbwanjam i vivama e ŇčgaliŇčgaliyaeko, na val…®kaiwae i utu. Na the ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® kururuwe val…®kaiwae i tagavavamareŇčgi.  
\v 16 Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye, thavala idanji lagh…®ye na thavala idanji nasiye, ravwenyevwenye na mbinyembinyeŇčgu, rakakaiwobwaga na rakarakayathuŇčgi, thetheghan mbwanjam theghewoniyema i vavothaŇčaŇčgi na e ghanjinono, i yaku e n…®manji e unenji o e ghamwanji.  
\v 17 ThoŇčgo lolo regha ma e ghanono ma val…®kaiwae i vamodo bigi regha o i vakuneŇča. Nonoko iyako thetheghan mbwanjam i vivama idae o nambako iya idaeko i woraŇčgiya.   
\p
\v 18 Mbene hu thimba amba ne val…®kaiwami hu thuweya idako iyako. ThoŇčgo regha nuwae i rumwaru, ambane i vaona tamweya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko iyako idae ghanamba, kaiwae nambako i woraŇčgiya lolo regha idae. Idae ghanamba iyake: 666.   
\c 14  
\s1 Sip Nariye na le ghar…®ghar…®  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya gh…®maraghaoko na ya thuweya Sip Nariye i ndeghath…® e Ou Saiyon vwatae, weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iya amalagh…®niye idae na Ramae idae th…® rori e ghamwanji lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiye wan handred poti po tausan (144,000).  
\v 2 Kaero ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i njama e buruburu Ňčgoreiya ŇčgonuŇčgo i vorunja e ghamwae varivariye laiye, na mb…®ler…® laiye lagh…®ye. Ghal…®ghal…®Ňča ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiya hap gharaŇčgaŇčga th…® Ňčge hap na ghal…®Ňčae.  
\v 3 Rawothuwothuko th…® ndeghath…® na ghamwanji i ghembeya ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko, thetheghan theghevar…®ko, na giyagiyako na th…® wo wothu togha regha th…® wothuŇča. Wothuko iyako ma te val…®kaiwae lolo i ghareghare na i wothuŇča, mbe iyaeŇčge vara ghar…®ghar…®ma Ňčgoreiye wan handred poti po tausan…®ma (144,000), thiye Loi kaerova i vamodonjoghaŇčgi yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji.  
\v 4 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake ma th…® vambigh…®ya ghanjimberegha e yathima thanavuniye, th…® kakaleva. Sip Nariye aŇčga i reŇča th…® rakambele. Thiye Loi kaerova i vamodo njoghaŇčgi yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji, na thiye th…® tabo wabwi iviva Loi na Sip Nariye weŇčgi.  
\v 5 Ma kwan mun i raŇčgima e ghaenji, na ma e ghanjiwonjowe.   
\s1 Nyao thovuthovuye thegheto lenji utuutu  
\p
\v 6 Na mbowo ya thuweva nyao thovuye regha i yoyo e lughawoghawoko, i wo toto thovuye memeghabananiye na i yathu weŇčgiya yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye ‚ÄĒ vanautuma na vanautuma weŇčgi, uu na uu weŇčgi, ghal…®ghal…®Ňča na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča weŇčgi, na ririwo na ririwo weŇčgi.  
\v 7 Na i dage e ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúHu mararu Loi na hu tarawe idae, kaiwae ghambaŇča i vanivaŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® kaero i vutha. Hu kururuwe, kaiwae iye buruburu, yambane, njigh…® na mbwa th…® voruvoru ghanjiravakatha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Na nyao thovuye theghewoniye i yoreghamba weya mevivako na iŇča, ‚ÄúBabilon, ghen ghemba lagh…®ye, kaero u marakaraka, kaero u marakaraka. Ghen, yathima thanavuniye raraithar…® e t…®ne u vakatha weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® wolagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya th…® muna waen vur…®vur…®ghegheniye na i vakowanaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 I njana mbowo reghava, nyao thovuye theghetoninji, tembe i yoreghambava theghewoma e ghereinji, na i kula ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúThela i kururu weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma na ŇčgaliŇčgaliyaeko, na ghanono ina e ghamwae o e n…®mae,  
\v 10 ne i gham…®no Loi le gaith…® gham…®nae. Le gaith…®ko iyako Ňčgoreiya waen vur…®vur…®ghegheniye moli kaero i liŇčgi e kom na i giyawe i mun. Iye ne i vaidiya v…®r…®niye e nd…®ghe ‚ÄĒ var…® salp i rara e t…®ne, le nyao thovuthovuye boboma na Sip Nariye e maranji.  
\v 11 Na nd…®gheko iya i vakatha v…®r…®ko weŇčgi munduwae i vorovoro mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako. Thavala th…® kururu weya thetheghan mbwanjam weiye ŇčgaliŇčgaliya, o thoŇčgo idae ghanono ina weŇčgi, gougou na ghararagh…®ye mane th…® towo e v…®r…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Iyake gharumwaru ‚ÄĒ RaloŇčweloŇčweghath…®, thavala th…® ghambugha Loi le mbaro na th…® loŇčweghath…®gha Jisas, weinji lenji riwouda th…® ghataŇčaghath…®.   
\p
\v 13 Amba ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i njama e buruburu iŇča, ‚ÄúU roriya iyake: I ri e mbaŇčake iyake na i ghaoko e ghamwandako, thavala thiye raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® na th…® mare, ghanjithovuye i lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ  
\p Nyao Boboma i golambo iŇča, ‚ÄúKo mbwana, thiye ne th…® towo lenji rovur…®gheghe e t…®ne, kaiwae lenji kaiwo modae mane i kwara, ina weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Yambaneke ghauloulo  
\p
\v 14 Amba ya gh…®maraghaoko na ya thuweya Ňčgal…®l…® kakaleva regha, na iya i yaku e vwataeko ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya lolo nariye,\x - \xo 14:14 \xt Dan 7:13\x* umbaliye ghamatabwaya th…® vakatha e gol ina e umbaliye, kaina wit ghagheten, marae i lawe moli, i lawe e n…®mae.  
\v 15 Na nyao thovuye regha mbowo i raŇčgimava Loi ele Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne, kaero i kula ghaoko weya iya i yakuma e Ňčgal…®l…®ko vwatae na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúYambaneke une kaero i mweghe. U wo len kainana na u ten, kaiwae uloulo ghambaŇča kaero i vutha.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 Kaero iya i yakuma e Ňčgal…®l…®ko vwatae i vakaiwoŇča le kainako e yambaneke, na i vathevao yambaneke ghauloulo.   
\p
\v 17 Na mbowo ya thuweva nyao thovuye regha i raŇčgima e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne e buruburu, amalagh…®niye tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, kaina gheten…®te, mara lawelaweniye ina e n…®mae.  
\v 18 Amba nyao thovuye reghava, iye nd…®ghe gharanjimbukiki, i raŇčgima e ghamba vowo, kaero i kula ghaoko weya gheuma iya kaina maraema lawelaweniye inawe, ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúU wo le kainana iya maraena lawelaweniye, u tena waen kwariŇčgina na u bigiŇčgima yambane e ghawaena r…®ghenji, kaiwae unenjina kaero th…® Ňčgwe.‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 Kaero nyaoma thovuye i vakaiwoŇča le kaina e yambaneke, i ten…®Ňčgiya yambaneke waen…®niye na i mban…®Ňčgi. Amba i bigiyathuŇčgi e ghamba imb…®imb…® lagh…®ye t…®ne, na ghamba imb…®imb…®ko iyako Loi le ghatemuru.  
\v 20 Amba th…® vur…®njoŇčanjoŇča waen…®ma e ghamba imb…®imb…®ma t…®ne e ghembako ghagana ghereiye, ko amba madibe i voru raŇčgi e ghamba imb…®imb…®ko t…®ne, na le voruko ve wo le bwagabwaga Ňčgoreiya tu handred kilomita, na le gheghenenja mbalama i wo wan na hap mitas.   
\c 15  
\s1 Nyao thovuthovuye th…® womena dagabora momouniye e yambaneke  
\p
\v 1 Amba mbowo ya thuweva nono lagh…®ye regha e buruburu, na ghayamoyamoko mbema i tomethi vara moli: nyao thovuthovuye ghepir…® ne th…® womena dagabora le ghanaghanagha ghepir…® e yambaneke, na dagaborako ghepir…®ninji iyako Loi le ghatemuru momouniye.   
\p
\v 2 Kaero ya thuweya bigi regha ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya njigh…®ko t…®ne marambwelambwelawae, th…® basi weiye nd…®ghe, amba thiyeko iya th…® kivwala thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma, na ŇčgaliŇčgaliya na iya amalagh…®niye idae e ghanambako. Ya thuweya th…® ndeghath…® e njigh…®ko ghadidiye na th…® ndembaŇčgiya hap Loi i bigigiya weŇčgi.  
\v 3 Amba th…® wothuŇča Loi le rakakaiwo Mosese ghawothu na Sip Nariye ghawothu th…®Ňča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúGiya Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye,  
\q1 len vakatha lagh…®lagh…®ye ghamba numowo.  
\q1 Yambaneke lagh…®ye lenji KiŇča ghen,  
\q1 ghan…®thanavu i rumwaru na i emunjoru.   
\q1
\v 4 Loi, ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® mararuŇčge,  
\q1 na th…® wovavwenyevwenyeŇča idan,  
\q1 kaiwae ghen ghan…®mberegha u boboma.  
\q1 Vanautumake wolagh…®ye th…® mena th…® kururu e ghen,  
\q1 kaiwae kaero th…® thuweya len vakatha i rumwaru.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 MbaŇča iyako iko, ya gh…®mara voro e buruburu na ya thuweya Ňägolo Boboma iye Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye, i mavu.  
\v 6 Amba nyao thovuthovuye ghepir…®ma, iya th…® womena dagaborama ghepir…®, th…® raŇčgima e Ňägolo Bobomako t…®ne. Th…® njimbo kwama thovuye th…® ndalandala, na mborowanji gheva gol th…® Ňčgar…® e gharenji vwata.  
\v 7 Amba thetheghan theghevar…®ma regha, i giya gaeba gol le ghanaghanagha ghepir…®, weŇčgiya nyaoko thovuthovuye ghepir…®. E gaebako thiyako t…®nenji Loi memeghabananiye le ghatemuru i riyevanjara.  
\v 8 Loi le vur…®gheghe na le vwenyevwenye Ňčgoreiya mundu, i riyevanjara Ňägolo Bobomako t…®ne, na ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha i ru e t…®neko, ghaghad nyaoko thovuthovuye ghepir…® th…® vakathavao dagabora ghepir…®ma.   
\c 16  
\s1 Dagabora ghepir…® nyao thovuthovuye th…® liŇčginjoŇča e yambaneke  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®ye regha i mena e Ňägolo Bobomako, i dage weŇčgiya nyaoko thovuthovuye ghepir…® iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa vohu liŇčginjoŇča e yambane Loi le ghatemuru iya ina e gaebako ghepir…®ko t…®nenji.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 2 Kaero nyaoko i vivako i wa ve liŇčgiya le gaebako une e yambane, amba thighathigha raraithar…® v…®r…®v…®r…®niye th…® yomara weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® iya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma ghanono ina weŇčgi na th…® kururu weya ŇčgaliŇčgaliyama.   
\p
\v 3 Na nyaoko theghewoniye i liŇčgiya le gaebako une e njigh…®ko t…®ne, njigh…®ko i gharav…® na madibe Ňčgoreiya lolo i mare mad…®bae, na njigh…®ko matemate e yawayawalinji thiya marevao.   
\p
\v 4 Na nyaoko thovuye theghetoninji i liŇčgiya le gaebako une e mbwa i voruvoru na e mbwarowou, kaero th…® gharav…® na madibe.  
\v 5 Kaero ya loŇčweya nyao thovuye mbwako ghanjiranjimbunjimbu ghal…®Ňčae iŇča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúLoi Boboma, ghen mbe inan…®we noroke na mbaŇča va i vivako, len lith…®ke iyake i thovuye moli.   
\q1
\v 6 Kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® va th…® vakatha raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko na ghal…®Ňčana gharautu mad…®banji i voru, i thovuye eŇčge u giya madibe weŇčgi na th…® mun.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Amba tembe ya loŇčweva ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i mena e ghamba vowoko iŇča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúMbwana, Giya Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye Moli, len lith…®ko i emunjoru na i rumwaru moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Kaero nyaoma theghevar…®ninji i liŇčgiya le gaeba une e varaeko. Loi i vatomwe weya varaeko na dayaghae i vur…®gheghe moli na i ŇčambuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.  
\v 9 Dayaghaeko i ŇčambuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, na iyako kaiwae th…® utuvathar…® weya Loi idae, iye dagaborako thiyako i mbaroŇčaŇčgi. Na othembe iyako ma th…® ndeghereiyewana lenji thar…® na th…® wovavwenyevwenyeŇča.   
\p
\v 10 Na nyaoko thovuye theghelimaninji i liŇčgiya le gaeba une e thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma le ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye, na i vakatha le ghamba mbaroko i momouwo. Ghar…®ghar…® th…® r…®gh…®mbiya maminji v…®r…®ko kaiwae.  
\v 11 Amba th…® utuvathar…® weya Loi e buruburu idae, kaiwae th…® ghataŇča v…®r…® na thiya thighathigha. Ko iyemaeŇčge othembe iyako ma th…® ndeghereiye wanaŇčgiya lenji thar…®.   
\p
\v 12 Amba nyaoko thovuye ghewonaninji i liŇčgiya le gaeba une e Walagh…®ta lagh…®ye Yupreitis. Kaero mbwako i meme na i vakatha kamwath…® mbala yavorowoko ghakiŇč ne th…® reŇčawe.  
\v 13 Kaero ya thuweya nyao raraithar…® thegheto, ghanjiyamoyamo Ňčgoreiya vwak…®rak…®ra, th…® raŇčgima mwatama lagh…®ye e ghae, thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma e ghae, na ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan e ghae.  
\v 14 Nyaoko raraithar…® thiyako th…® vakatha vakatha vavana na th…® raka weŇčgiya yambaneke ghakiŇč weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ragagaith…® na th…® vaŇčguvathavathaŇčgi. Na thiye th…® vivatha na weinji Loi th…® gaith…® weya Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye Moli e ghambaŇča lagh…®ye t…®ne.   
\p
\v 15 Giya iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! Lo menake Ňčgoreiya rakaiv…® lenji mena! Thela ne i njaŇčanjaŇča na i vivatha nonowo ghakwama, ne i vaidiya thovuye, amba mane i bukabuka na i monjina ghar…®ghar…® e maranji.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Amba nyaoko raraithar…® th…® vaŇčguvathavathaŇčgiya kiŇč…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghemba idae vaŇča Hibru th…®Ňča Amagedon e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 17 Amba nyaoko thovuye ghepir…®ninji i liŇčgiya le gaebako une e lughawoghawoko. Kaero ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®ye regha i raŇčgima e Ňägolo Bobomako e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero iko.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 Kaero i vivilema na mb…®ler…® lalainji, na ragheragheghe vur…®vur…®ghegheniye i yomara. I ri mbaŇčaniye Loi i bigiraweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e yambaneke na ghaghada mbaŇčakoko ma mbaŇča regha mbarimbariri Ňčgoreiyako i yomara, ko iyemaeŇčge mbarimbaririko iyako i vur…®gheghe lagh…®ye moli.  
\v 19 Babilon, ghemba idae lagh…®ye, i maviya na gheth…®to, na val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye ghembaghembaninji lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® marakaraka. Loi mbe i renuwaŇčakiki eŇčge Babilon, ghemba idae lagh…®ye, amba e ghakomuko t…®ne waen i riyevanjara, i th…®n…®giyawe na i mun, iyako amalagh…®niye le ghatemuru.  
\v 20 Raurauke wolagh…®ye na ououke wolagh…®ye mbema th…® ghawe vara.  
\v 21 Uye umbwara iya Ňčgoreiya var…®ma, vuyowanji lagh…®ye moli Ňčgoreiya poti paeb kilo th…® dobunjama e lughawoghawoko na th…® unja ghar…®ghar…® e vwatanji. Amba ghar…®ghar…® th…® utuvathar…® weya Loi kaiwae i variya vuyowo Ňčgoreiyako weŇčgi. Kaiwae vuyowoko iyako i thar…® lagh…®ye moli.   
\c 17  
\s1 Wevo rayathiyathima na thetheghan mbwanjam  
\p
\v 1 Amba nyaoma thovuye theghepir…®ma iya th…® mbana gaebama ghepir…®ma regha i mena i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u mena na wo ya vatomwe e ghen Loi ne ŇčgoroŇčga na i lith…® weya wevo iye rayathiyathima moli, i yaku e mbwa vwatanji.  
\v 2 Yambaneke ghakiŇč…®Ňčgi weinji th…® vakatha yathima thanavuniye, na rameyambane th…® muna le waen na th…® kabaleya. Waen…®ko iyako Ňčgoreiya le yathimako thanavuniye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 Amba Nyao Boboma le vur…®gheghe e t…®ne na nyao thovuye i yowoŇčgo e njamnjam. Na gheke va thuweya wevo eunda, i yaku e thetheghan mbwanjam sosoro regha e vwatae. Thetheghan…®ko iyako umbaliye le ghanaghanagha ghepir…® na ghasokisoki hoyaworo. Tomethi ida th…® rori e riwaeko wolagh…®ye, na idako thiyako th…® utuvathar…® weya Loi.  
\v 4 Wevoko iyako i njimbo kwama sosoro marae i bwedi na sosoro moli, na riwae ghaghavatha gol, var…® th…® ndalandala, na Ňčgile modanji lagh…®ye. I th…®na ndegh…® th…® vakatha e gol, na e t…®ne, ghathanavu raithar…® moli na yathima thanavuniye raraithar…® i riyevanjara.  
\v 5 E ghamwae th…® roriya ida reghawe, na idako iyako ghaghareghare i rothuwele, Ňčgoreiyake: ‚ÄúBabilon, ghemba idae lagh…®ye, wanakauko thiya th…® vamodo riwanji na raithar…®thar…®ko wolagh…®ye t…®nanjiya ghen.‚ÄĚ  
\v 6 Ya thuweya wevoko iyako i muna raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® na Jisas utuniye gharayathu mad…®banji na i kabaleyaŇča.  
\p MbaŇča ma thuwe mbema i wovara nuwaŇčgu.  
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge nyaoma thovuye i vaitoŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae i wo nuwan? Wo ya vaghareŇčge wevoko na thetheghan mbwanjam sosoroko umbaliye ghepir…® na ghasokisoki hoyaworo iya i thakowe ghanjisimosimo moli na u loŇčwe.  
\v 8 Thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko iya mo thuweko iye va i vivako inawe, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčake kaero nandere, na amba tene i menava e gogako iya i ghenenja moliko e t…®ne, na i wa ghamukuwo kaiwae. Ghar…®ghar…® thiya yayaku e yambaneke, thavala idaidanji ma th…® rorinjoŇča yawal…® e ghabuk t…®ne amba muyai va i vakatha yambaneke, ne gharenji i yo lagh…®ye mbaŇča ne th…® thuweya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko. Va i vivako inawe, mbaŇčake kaero nandere na mbaŇča i menamenako ne i yomara.   
\p
\v 9 ‚Äú(Iyake nuwaiya thimba na nuwarumwaru ambane hu ghareghare bigibigike thiyake.) Thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko iya umbaliye ghepir…®ko, thiye Ňčgoreiya bobokulu ghepir…®\f + \fr 17:9 \ft Bobokuluko ghepir…®ko th…® meth…® ghemba lagh…®ye Rom. Idake Babilon gheke Ňčgoreiye ida unouno Rom kaiwae.\f* iya wevoko i yaku e vwata, na umbaliyeko ghepir…® tembe Ňčgoranjiya kiŇč theghepir…®,  
\v 10 theghelima kaero th…®ko, regha mbe inawe i mbaro, na ghepir…®ninji amba ma i mena. MbaŇča ne i mena, ne i mbaro mbaŇča ubotu moli.  
\v 11 Thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma iya mbaŇča va i vivako inawe, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčake kaero nandere, iye kiŇč lenji ghanaghanagha ghepir…®ma theghewaninji. Kaero i loŇčgaloŇčga ghavakowana kaiwae.   
\p
\v 12 ‚ÄúSokisokina yaworo iya mo thuwena th…® meth…® kiŇč theyaworo, na amba ma ghanjimbaŇča th…® mbaro, ko iyemaeŇčge ne th…® wo vur…®gheghe na th…® tabo kiŇč na th…® mbaro weinji thetheghan mbwanjam ma mbaŇča ubotu moli.  
\v 13 KiŇč…®Ňčgiko thiyako lenji renuwaŇčako ne regha, na lenji vur…®gheghe na lenji mbaro ne th…® vatomwe weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko.  
\v 14 Ne weinji Sip Nariye th…® gaith…®, ko iyemaeŇčge Sip Nariye ne weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu, thiye Loi va i tuthiŇčgi na i kula weŇčgi na th…® loŇčweghath…® vur…®gheghewe ne th…® kivwalaŇčgi. Kaiwae Sip Nariye iye giyagiya ghanji Giya, na kiŇč lenji KiŇč.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 Nyaoma thovuye i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúMbwako iya mo thuweŇčgiko, iya wevo rayathiyathimako me yaku e vwatanji, thiye Ňčgoranjiya vanautuma tomethi na tomethi, wabwi tomethi na tomethi, ririwo tomethi na tomethi na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča tomethi na tomethi.  
\v 16 Na sokisokiko iya mo thuweŇčgi hoyaworoko, ne weinji thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma th…® th…®gh…®yawana wevo rayathiyathimama. Ne th…® vakowana na th…® bigivao le bigibigi na th…® roitete bukabuka. Ne th…® ghana riwae na th…® Ňčambuyathu e nd…®ghe.  
\v 17 Kaiwae Loi kaero i woraweya renuwaŇča e gharenjiko na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya amalagh…®niye le renuwaŇča, na lenji renuwaŇča regha, th…® woraweya lenji mbaro weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma, ghaghad Loi le utu i tabo emunjoru.  
\v 18 Wevoko iya mo thuweko iye Ňčgoreiya ghemba idae lagh…®ye na i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya yambaneke ghakiŇč…®Ňčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\c 18  
\s1 Babilon i marakaraka  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča nyaoma thovuye i utuvao, kaero ya thuweva nyao thovuye regha i njama e buruburuko. Mbaro vur…®vur…®ghegheniye inawe na le vwenyevwenye manjamanjalawae i vawoya yambaneke lagh…®ye.  
\v 2 Amba i kula na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye moli iŇča, ‚ÄúBabilon, ghembako iyako ida lagh…®ye, kaero i marakaraka, kaero i marakaraka! Kaero i tabo nyao raraithar…® ghambanji, na ma ghanjithanavu raraithar…® moli ghambanji.  
\v 3 Kaiwae le yathimako thanavuniye Ňčgoreiya waen vur…®vur…®ghegheniye yambaneke wolagh…®ye th…® mun na i vakowanaŇčgi. KiŇč e yambaneke th…® vakatha yathima thanavuniye weinji, na rakunekuneke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke lagh…®ye th…® vaidiya lenji vwenyevwenye, kaiwae nuwaeko i ghaŇčgowa bigibigi modanji lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Na mbowo ya loŇčweva ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i njama e buruburu iŇča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúGhemi lo ghar…®ghar…® hu rakaiteta ghembana iyana!  
\q1 Ne hu ndewo le vakathana raithar…® thanavuniye,  
\q1 mbala ma ghalith…®na mun regha i ghao e ghemi.   
\q1
\v 5 Kaiwae le thar…®ko i vala e vwatae ve wo buruburuko  
\q1 na ghathanavuko raraithar…® Loi mbe i renuwaŇčakiki eŇčge, tene i lith…®we.   
\q1
\v 6 The vakatha i vakatha e ghen, ghen tembe u vakathaweva.  
\q1 Na le vakathako modae, hu vakathath…®we na ma e vwataeva.  
\q1 I giya waen vur…®vur…®ghegheniye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® mun,  
\q1 iya kaiwae hu giyawe waen vur…®vur…®ghegheniye moli na i mun.   
\q1
\v 7 I wovoreŇča idae, na i yakuyaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne,  
\q1 iya kaiwae modae hu giya v…®r…® lagh…®yewe na i randaranda.  
\q1 Wevoke iŇča,  
\q1 ‚ÄėGhino kwin na ya mbaro,  
\q1 ghino ma wambwi Ňčgoreiye,  
\q1 na ma mbaŇča regha ya randaranda Ňčgoreiya wambwiwambwi ghanjithanavu.‚Äô   
\q1
\v 8 Iyako kaiwae, ne mbaŇča regha e t…®ne  
\q1 ko amba ghadagabora th…® yomara, Ňčgoreiye  
\q1 ghambwera, randa na bada lagh…®ye moli.  
\q1 Elagh…®niye ne i nda e nd…®ghe une,  
\q1 kaiwae Giya Loi, iya i lith…®kowe, iye Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye Moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 ‚ÄúYambaneke ghakiŇč…®Ňčgi, thavala va weinji th…® yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne na th…® vakatha yathima thanavuniye, ne th…® raŇčivetho lagh…®ye moli, mbaŇča ne th…® thuweya i ndako na munduwae.  
\v 10 Mbene th…® ndeghath…® bwagabwaga moliwe, ne iwaeŇčge th…® vaidiya ghav…®r…®ko, na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėO thar…®! O thar…®! Babilon, ghemba idae lagh…®ye na ghemba vur…®vur…®ghegheniye, mbaŇča ubotu moli e t…®ne kaero ghanlith…® ghan…®mbaŇča i mena.‚Äô   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúRakunekune e yambaneke thiye tembe th…® raŇčiva, kaiwae ma tembe lolo reghava ne i vamodo lenji bigibigiko.  
\v 12 Ma lolo regha ne i vamoda weŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake: gol, silva, var…® ghanjiyamoyamo i thovuye na Ňčgile; kwama thovuye, kwama mara pepol, kwama silk\f + \fr 18:12 \ft Kwama silk iye modae lagh…®ye moli vara.\f* na kwama marae sosoro; umbwa butiye thovuye, bigibigi th…® vakathaŇčgi elepant e ghasokisoki\f + \fr 18:12 \ft VaŇča lumo th…® uno elepant ghasokisoki ‚ÄúIvory.‚ÄĚ\f*, bigibigi th…® vakathaŇčgi e umbwaumbwa modanji lagh…®ye, thiye th…® vakathaŇčgi e kopa, thiye th…® vakathaŇčgi e aiyan na thiye th…® vakathaŇčgi e var…® th…® ndalandala;  
\v 13 sinamon, bunama butiye thovuye, bunama mer na preŇčkinisen…®s\f + \fr 18:13 \ft PreŇčkinisen…®s na mer umbwaumbwa thinji butinji thovuye na modanji lagh…®ye moli.\f*; waen na oliv…® bunamaniye; wit na pwalawa; burumwaka, sip, hos na sariyot. Tembe th…® vakuneŇčaŇčgiva ghar…®ghar…®.  
\v 14 Rakunekune ne th…® dagewe na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėVwenyevwenyena bigibiginiye, iya u rerenuwaŇča kaiwanjina na mbala inanji e ghen, kaero thiya ghawevao, na len bigibigina na le vwenyevwenyena wolagh…®ye kaero th…® rakaiteteŇčge, ma te val…®kaiwaeva u biginjoghaŇčgi.‚Äô   
\p
\v 15 ‚ÄúRakunekune thavala th…® vavakune lenji bigibigiwe na th…® vaidiya lenji bigibigi lemoyowe, mbe th…® mararuva ne iwaeŇčge tembe th…® vaidiva v…®r…®ko va i vaidiko. Iya kaiwae mbe th…® ndeghath…® bwagabwaga moli na th…® randa lagh…®ye  
\v 16 th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėO thar…®! O thar…®! Babilon, ghemba idae lagh…®ye, va u njimbo kwama marae pepol na marae sosoro, na riwana ghaghavatha gol, var…® ghanjiyamoyamo i ndalandala, na Ňčgile modanji lagh…®ye.  
\v 17 MbaŇča ubotu moli ghanlith…®gh…® va i vutha, na len vwenyevwenyeko bigibiginiye wolagh…®ye thiya ghawevao.‚Äô  
\p ‚ÄúWaŇčga gharauluuluko wolagh…®ye, weinjiyaŇčgiya waŇčgako gharathatha na gharakakaiwo, na thiye lenji mani le ghamba mena th…® kaiwo e njigh…®, mbe th…® ndeghath…® bwagabwaga moli.  
\v 18 Ne th…® thuweya i rako na munduwae, amba th…® kula lagh…®ye moli th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėThare mbaŇča regha ghemba regha idae lagh…®ye ina ghena?‚Äô  
\v 19 Amba th…® yathuvoreŇča vugha e umbalinji, na th…® randa lagh…®ye th…®Ňča,  
\q1 ‚ÄėO thar…®! O thar…®! Babilon, ghemba idae lagh…®ye, waŇčgako tatanuwagae wolagh…®ye th…® vaidiya lenji bigibigi lemoyo moli e len vwenyevwenyena t…®ne. MbaŇča ubotu moli e t…®ne, len bigibigina wolagh…®ye thiya ghawevao!   
\q1
\v 20 Ghemi rameburuburu, huya warari!  
\q1 Ghemi raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®, weimiyaŇčgiya ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® na ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, huya warari  
\q1 kaiwae thar…®ko iya Babilon va th…® vakathako e ghemi, ghath…®th…® Loi kaero i vakathanjoghawe.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Kaero nyao thovuye vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha i wo var…® lagh…®ye regha Ňčgoreiya pwalawa ghaghevwaŇčgoŇčgo, i du na ve unja e njigh…®ko t…®ne, na iŇča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúBabilon, ghemba idae lagh…®ye,  
\q1 tene th…® duŇčge na Ňčgoreiyako,  
\q1 na mane te ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuweŇčgeva.   
\q1
\v 22 Ghe mwadimwadiwo Ňčgoranjiya hap, igo na mema ghal…®Ňčanji mane te th…® yomarava e ghen.  
\q1 Thavala e lenji ghareghare kaiwo tomethi na tomethi kaiwanji, ma tene th…® yakuva e ghen.  
\q1 Pwalawa ghaghamba vwaŇčgoŇčgo laiye ma tene ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweva e ghen.   
\q1
\v 23 Kad…®ŇčeŇče manjamanjalawae mane te i woyava e ghen,  
\q1 na ragheghe gh…®moru weiye ghaghaivaun wevo, mane te ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweva ghal…®Ňčanji e ghen.  
\q1 Ghan…®lith…® ne Ňčgoreiyako, kaiwae va ghan…®rakunekune th…® vakatha idanji lagh…®ye e yambaneke,  
\q1 na len kukurana e t…®ne u yaroŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke.   
\q1
\v 24 Loi ne i lith…® e ghen kaiwae va u tagavavamareŇčgiya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu na raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko,  
\q1 na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye va thiya mare e yambaneke, ghanjigaith…® modae i lith…® na i ghao e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\c 19  
\p
\v 1 Iyako e ghereiye, ya loŇčweya wabwi lagh…®ye ghal…®Ňčanji e buruburu, ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye moli th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAleluiya!\f + \fr 19:1 \ft MbaŇča Jiu va nuwanjiya th…® taraweŇča Loi, th…® yaro na th…®Ňča ‚ÄúAleluiya!‚ÄĚ Iyake Hibru lenji utu gharumwaru ra tarawe Loi.\f* Ra tarawe Loi! Vamoru na vwenyevwenye na vur…®gheghe ina weya la Loi,  
\v 2 kaiwae le vavaniva i emunjoru na i rumwaru. Loi kaero i vanivaŇča wevoma rayathiyathimama moli na i lith…®we, kaiwae le yathimako thanavuniye e t…®ne i vakowana yambaneke. I gaboŇčgiya Loi le rakakaiwo ghath…®th…® i vakatha njoghawe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 Mbowo th…® kulava mbaŇčaiwoniye th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAleluiya! Ra tarawe Loi. Babilon i nda na munduwae mbene i mundumundu voro vara yandiri yandewa.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Amba giyagiya theiwo na theghevar…®ma weinjiyaŇčgiya thetheghan theghevar…®ma, th…® ronja e gheghenji vuvuye na th…® kururu weya Loi, iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyema. Kaero th…® kula th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwana. Ňägoreiye. Ra tarawe Loi! Aleluiya!‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Sip Nariye le ghe ghathaga  
\p
\v 5 Amba ya loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i mena e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi Loi le rakakaiwo na le ghar…®ghar…® taulagh…®na ghemi thavala hu yavwatatawana, nasiye na lagh…®ye, hu tarawe la Loi!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 Kaero ya loŇčweya wabwi lagh…®ye moli ghal…®Ňčanji Ňčgoreiya ŇčgonuŇčgo laiye na mb…®ler…® laiye th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAleluiya! Ra tarawe Loi! Kaiwae Giya Loi iye Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye Moli, na iye rambarombaro.  
\v 7 Ra warari, nuwanda i thovuye, na ra wovavwenyevwenyeŇča Loi! Kaiwae Sip Nariye ghambaŇča ghe kaero i vutha, na ghaghaivaun wevoniye kaero i vivathavao ghe kaiwae.  
\v 8 Loi i ligiya weya kwama kakaleva na marambwelambwelawae i njimbo.‚ÄĚ (Kwama kakalevako iyako gharumwaru raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® lenji vakatha i rumwaru.)   
\p
\v 9 Amba nyao thovuye i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúU rori Ňčgoreiyake, ‚ÄėThavala Loi i kula vathaŇčgi na th…® ru Sip Nariye le gheko ghathaga e t…®ne, Loi i vawarariŇčgaŇčgi lagh…®ye moli.‚Äô‚ÄĚ Na i njana mbowo iŇčava, ‚ÄúThiyake utuutu emunjoru th…® mena weya Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 MbaŇča ya loŇčweya iyako, ya ronja e ghegheŇčgu vuvuye na ya munje ya kururuwe, ko iyemaeŇčge i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúThava! Ghino mbema rakakaiwo eŇčge, ŇčgoraŇčgwa ghen na len val…®raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®, thavala th…® utuŇča Jisas utuniye thovuye. U kururuwe eŇčge Loi kaiwae Loi Une iya i giya weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vur…®vur…®ghegheko na val…®kaiwae th…® utuŇča Jisas utuutuniye.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Lolo regha i tha e hos kakaleva  
\p
\v 11 Amba ya thuweya buruburu i mavu na gheko hos kakaleva i ndeghath…®. Iya i rovathe i vwataeko idae th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVarevareminjeniye moli na Emunjoru.‚ÄĚ E le niva na ele gaith…® t…®nenji weiye le vakatha rumwarumwaruniye.  
\v 12 Maramarae Ňčgoreiya nd…®ghe mamiye na umbaliye ghamatabwaya lemoyo. Idae va th…® rori e riwae, na idako iyako ma lolo regha i ghareghare ko mbe ghamberegha eŇčge i ghareghare gharumwaru.  
\v 13 Ghakwama molao mbe madibe eŇčge, na idae iyake, ‚ÄúLoi Ghal…®Ňčae.‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 Ragagaith…® e buruburu th…® rakareghambawe, th…® njimboŇčgiya kwama thovuthovuye kakaleva na i th…®na na th…® rakatha e hos kakaleva.  
\v 15 I raŇčgima e ghae gaith…® ghaghalith…® mare lawelaweniye, ne i gaith…®we na i kivwalaŇčgiya vanautumake wolagh…®ye, na weiye le vur…®ghegheko wolagh…®ye i mbaroŇčaŇčgi. Iye ne i vur…®njoŇčaŇčgi Ňčgoreiye lolo regha i vur…®njoŇča waen uneune e ghamba imb…®imb…® t…®ne. Ne i vakatha iyako kaiwae Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye le ghatemuru lagh…®ye moli weŇčgi.  
\v 16 E ghakwama molao na e vavae th…® roriya ida reghawe, gharorori Ňčgoreiyake, ‚ÄúKiŇč lenji KiŇč na giyagiya ghanji Giya.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Amba ya thuweya nyao thovuye regha i ndeghath…® e varaeko t…®ne, na i kula weŇčgiya mako wolagh…®ye, iya th…® yoyo e lughawoghawoko, e ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúHu rakamena hu mevathavatha Loi le thaga lagh…®ye kaiwae.  
\v 18 Na hu ghana kiŇč, kin mara mbouye na ragagaith…® mbun…®maninji, na hu ghan hos na thavala th…® tha e vwatanji mbun…®maninji, na hu ghana ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye, thavala rakakaiwobwaga na rakarakayathuŇčgi, thavala idanji nasiye na thavala idanji lagh…®ye mbun…®maninji.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 19 Amba mbowo ya thuweŇčgiyava thetheghan mbwanjam na yambaneke ghakiŇč…®Ňčgi weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ragagaith…® th…® mevathavatha, na th…® gaith…® weŇčgiya iya i tha e hos…®ma vwatae weiyaŇčgiya le ragagaith…®ma.  
\v 20 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® laweŇčgiya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma weiye ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan na th…® Ňčgar…®Ňčgi. Ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan…®ko va i vakathaŇčgiya vakatha ghamba rotaele vavana thetheghan mbwanjam…®ko kaiwae, na e t…®ne i yaroŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, iya thavala thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma ghanono ina weŇčgi na th…® kururu weya ŇčgaliŇčgaliyako. Amba th…® mban…®Ňčgiya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma weiye ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan…®ma, mbe e yawayawalinji, th…® bigiyathu njoŇčaŇčgi e nd…®ghema ghagoga t…®ne, iya var…® salpa mbe i raramawe vara.  
\v 21 Iya i tha e hos…®ma i govavamareŇčgiya lenji ragagaith…®ma e kaina iya me raŇčgima e ghaeko. Kaero mako wolagh…®ye iya th…® yoyoko th…® mena th…® ghana mbun…®maninji ghaghada val…®kaiwanji.   
\c 20  
\s1 Th…® Ňčgar…®ghath…®gha Seitan theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…® (1000)  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya thuweya nyao thovuye regha i njama e buruburu, i th…®na ki e n…®mae, iya gogama iya i ghenenja moli ghaki na i th…®na sen lagh…®ye mbambara.  
\v 2 Kaero i wa ve laweya mwatama lagh…®ye, iye mwata mbe mevivako, idae th…®Ňča Devil o Seitan, na i Ňčgar…®rawe theghathegha le ghanaghanagha hoserithaŇčar…®.  
\v 3 Kaero i wokiyathunjoŇča e gogama iya i ghenenja moli t…®ne, i wovagumo e umbaliye na i monjevalawe e monjemonje. Mbowo i yaku gheko ghaghad theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…®, na thava i yaroŇčgiya val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye ghar…®ghar…®niye. Theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…® e ghereiye, amba th…® rakayathu, ko iyemaeŇčge le yaku mane molao moli.   
\p
\v 4 Amba tembe ya thuweŇčgiva ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye vavana. Ghar…®ghar…® va th…® utuŇča Jisas utuniye na th…® vavaghareŇča Loi ghal…®Ňčae na th…® gaboŇčgi, tembe ma thuweva unenji. Thiye ma mbaŇča regha th…® kururu weya thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma na ŇčgaliŇčgaliya, na ma ghanono ina e ghamwanji o e n…®manji. Kaero e yawayawalinji na th…® yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko, kaiwae Loi i giya vur…®gheghe weŇčgi na th…® mbaro. Kaero weinji Krais th…® mbaro theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…® e t…®ne.  
\v 5 Ramaremareko thiyako Loi va i vakathakai na e yawayawalinjiva. Wolagh…®yeko ne th…® thuweiru mbaŇča theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…® ne iko.  
\v 6 Ramaremareko iya nevole th…® thuweirukaiko Loi ne i vawarariŇčaŇčgi na le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye th…® boboma. Thiye mane th…® vaidiya mare theghewoniye le vur…®gheghe, ko iyemaeŇčge ne th…® tabo rakakaiwo boboma Loi na Krais kaiwanji. Thiye ne weinji Krais th…® mbaro theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…® regha e t…®ne.   
\s1 Th…® kivwala Seitan  
\p
\v 7 Theghathagha hoseriyethaŇčar…® ne iko na e ghereiye, ko amba th…® rakayathu Seitan e thiyoma t…®ne,  
\v 8 amba i raŇčgi na i wa e yambaneke lagh…®ye, weŇčgiya vanautumake thiyake, Gog na Magog,\f + \fr 20:8 \ft Gog na Magog th…® meth…® yambaneke lagh…®ye. Lenji gaith…® weinji Gog na Magog th…® utuŇčako Buk Teuye Isi 38:1‚Äď39:20.\f* na i yaroŇčgi. Na i mban…®vathavathaŇčgi gaith…® kaiwae, lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya kerakerako e njigh…®ko.   
\p
\v 9 Seitan weiyaŇčgiya le ragagaith…® ne th…® loŇčgaloŇčgaŇča na th…® ndegh…®liŇča ghembako Loi i gharethovu kaiwaeko, na iya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® th…® yakukowe. Ko iyemaeŇčge nd…®ghe ne i njama e buruburuko na i ŇčambuvaoŇčgi.  
\v 10 Amba Seitan, ghar…®ghar…® ghanjirakwan, ne th…® wokiyathunjoŇča e nd…®gheko i rarako weiye var…® salpa e t…®ne. Thetheghan mbwanjam…®ma weiye ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan kaerova th…® bigiyathu njoŇčaŇčgiwe iyako. Thiye weinji Seitan gougou na ghararagh…®ye ne th…® vaidiya v…®r…® ma ele ghambako.   
\s1 Loi le ghatha momouniye  
\p
\v 11 Amba ya thuweya Loi i yaku ele ghamba yaku lagh…®ye vwenyevwenye na i kakaleva. Na mbema e ghamwae eŇčge yambane na buruburu th…® roghawe na ma tembe ra thuweŇčgiva.  
\v 12 Kaero ya thuweŇčgiya ramaremare, thavala va e yambaneke idanji lagh…®ye na thavala ma e idaidanji thiya ndeghath…® e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko e ghamwae. Amba th…® tateŇčgiya buk, kaero Loi i vanivaŇčaŇčgiya i gorugoru weya lenji vakathako utuniye, iya bukuko th…® woraŇčgiya. Na mbowo th…® tateva buk regha, iyako yawal…® ghabuk.  
\v 13 Ghar…®ghar…® va th…® mare e njigh…® na thiye th…® yaku Mare e t…®ne na Thambe, th…® raka na veth…® ndeghath…® niva kaiwae. Na regha na regha Loi i vanivaŇčaŇčgi Ňčgoreiya lenji vakathako.  
\v 14 Amba Loi i bigiyathuŇčgiya Mare na Thambe e nd…®gheko i rarako t…®ne. E nd…®gheko i rarako t…®ne iye mare theghewoniye.  
\v 15 ThoŇčgo lolo regha ma th…® vaidiya idae yawal…® e ghabuk t…®ne, th…® wokiyathunjoŇča e nd…®gheko i rarako t…®ne.   
\c 21  
\s1 Jerusalem togha  
\p
\v 1 Amba ya thuweya buruburu togha na yambane togha. Buruburu teuye na yambane teuye kaero th…® ghawe, na njigh…® ma tembe inaweva.  
\v 2 Na mbowo ya thuweva Ghemba Boboma, Jerusalem togha, i njama weya Loi e buruburu. Iye Ňčgoreiya ragheghe wevo kaero i vivathavao, na i roroghagha weya gh…®moruko na th…® ghe.  
\v 3 Na tembe ya loŇčweva ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®ye regha i mena e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko t…®ne iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! Loi le ghamba yaku kaero ina weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, na amalagh…®niye i yaku e t…®nenji. Thiye th…® tabo le ghar…®ghar…®, amalagh…®niye ghamberegha ne i yaku weŇčgi na i tabo lenji Loi.  
\v 4 Ne i thavwiyathu maralumunjiko wolagh…®ye, ma tene mareva, ma randa na ma v…®r…®, kaiwae bigi teuyeke thiyake kaero iko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Amba iya i yaku e ghamba yaku vwenyevwenyeko iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! Bigibigike wolagh…®ye ya vatoghaŇčaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ Na tembe iŇčava, ‚ÄúUtuutuke thiyake u rorinjoŇčaŇčgi, kaiwae th…® emunjoru na val…®kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweghath…®.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 Kaero i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero iko! Ghino Alepa na Omega, ghino va Irikowe na ne Eleghambako. Thavala mbwa i ghar…®Ňčgi ne ya vatomwe weŇčgi na th…® muna mbwarowou i bwalabwala voroko, iya yawal…®ko ghembwa, na mbwako iyako ma e modamodae.  
\v 7 Thavala th…® ghataŇčaghath…® kaiwaŇčgu na th…® vur…®gheghe kivwalaŇčgiya thar…®ke wolagh…®ye, thovuyeko wolagh…®ye thiyako ne ya vatomwe weŇčgi, na ghino ne ya tabo lenji Loi na thiye th…® tabo lo ŇčgaŇčga.  
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge thavala lenji mararu eŇčge i yawoŇčgi, thavala ma th…® loŇčweghath…®, thavala th…® vakavakatha monjina thanavuniye, ragabo, rayathiyathima, kukura gharavakavakatha, thavala th…® kururu weya loi kwan…®kwan…®Ňčgi, na rakwan…®Ňčgike wolagh…®ye, thiya vara wolagh…®yeke thiyake ghambanjiya mbwarowouko iya var…® salpa i ravalaŇčakowe vara. Nd…®gheko iyako iye mare theghewoniye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Amba nyao theghepir…®ma iya th…® bigiya gaebama ghepir…® na dagabora momouniye th…® riyevanjara, regha i mena i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena na wo ya vatomwe e ghen ghaivaun wevoko, iya Sip Nariye levoko e ghen.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 Nyao Boboma le vur…®gheghe i ru e ghino na nyao thovuye i woŇčgo ya wa e ou lagh…®ye na memevoroniye regha vwatae. Kaero i vatomwe e ghino Ghemba Boboma, Jerusalem, i njama weya Loi e buruburu.  
\v 11 Loi le vwenyevwenye i vakeke ghembako iyako, na marambwelambwelawae i lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya var…® modae lagh…®ye jaspa, na marae i ndalandala Ňčgoreiya kanukanu marae.  
\v 12 Ghembako iyako ghagana i lagh…®ye na i mevoro, ghath…®n…®mba yaworo na ghewo, na nyao thovuthovuye theyaworo na theghewo th…® njimbukikiŇčgi. E th…®n…®mba regha na regha uu Isirel regha na regha idaidanji inawe.  
\v 13 Mbothiye i vorovorowoko ghagana ghath…®n…®mba thegheto, mbothiye i njanjawoko ghagana ghath…®n…®mba thegheto, mbothiye e yaghalako ghagana ghath…®n…®mba thegheto, e ghaiwabuko ghagana ghath…®n…®mba thegheto.  
\v 14 Var…® vur…®vur…®ghegheniye yaworo na ghewo th…® mban na ganako r…®ghe ghambagh…®mbagh…® na Sip Nariye ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® theyaworo na theghewo regha na regha th…® roriya idae e var…®ko regha na regha vwatae.   
\p
\v 15 Na nyaoko thovuye iya i utuutuko e ghino, i wo le gherughirughi th…® vakatha e gol, na i rughiya ghembako, ghaganako na ghath…®n…®mbako wolagh…®ye.  
\v 16 Ghembako i vagh…®liya mbe i mboromboro vara, ma t…®vot…® turaŇčgi, na le molamolao i mboromboro weiye le magamagaga. Nyaoko thovuye i wo le gherughirughi na i rughiya ghembako le molamolao Ňčgoreiya tu tausan tu handred (2,200) kilomita, na le magamagaga na le gheneghenevoro i mboromboro weiye le molamolaoko.  
\v 17 Te vambe i rughiva ghembako ghagana, le dubaduba sikisti paeb (65) mita. Gherughirughiko iyava i woko, va e mbaŇčako iyako ghar…®ghar…® mbe th…® vavakaiwoŇča.  
\v 18 Ganako va th…® vatad e var…® jaspa na ghemba t…®ne th…® vatad e gol une moli, marae i ndalandala Ňčgoreiya kanukanu.  
\v 19 Ghembako ghagana ghambagh…®mbagh…® th…® mban…®Ňčgiya tomethi var…® modanji lagh…®ye. Var…® iviva ganako regha iye jaspa, theghewoniye sapaya, theghetoniye ageit, ghevar…®niye var…® mbwaumbwau emerold,  
\v 20 ghelimaniye oniks, ghewonaniye kaniliyan, ghepir…®niye krisolait, ghewaniye beril, ghesiwoniye topas, yaworoniye kalsedoni, yaworo na regha jasin…®t, na yaworo na ghewoniye ametis.  
\v 21 Ghembako ghath…®n…®mba yaworo na ghewo th…® vakathaŇčgi e Ňčgile modanji lagh…®ye, yaworo na tembe ghewova. Th…®n…®mba regha na regha th…® vakatha e Ňčgileko iyako regha na regha. Ghembako ghakamwath…® th…® vakatha e gol une moli na marae i ndalandala Ňčgoreiya kanukanu.   
\p
\v 22 Ma ya thuwe mun Ňčgolo boboma regha e ghambako t…®ne, kaiwae Giya Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye Moli weiye Sip Nariye thiye ghambako iyako ghaŇčgolo boboma.  
\v 23 Ghembako ma e ghavarae na ma e ghamanjala na th…® giya manjamanjalawe, kaiwae Loi le vwenyevwenye manjamanjalawae i vakeke, na Sip Nariye iye ghakad…®ŇčeŇče.  
\v 24 Ghar…®ghar…® e val…®vaŇčga na val…®vaŇčga e yambaneke lagh…®ye th…® loŇčgaloŇčga e ghambako manjamanjalawae, na yambaneke ghakiŇč…®Ňčgi th…® bigimena lenji gogomwau bigibiginiye e t…®ne.  
\v 25 Ghararagh…®yeke wolagh…®ye ghembako ghath…®n…®mbaŇčgi ma th…® k…®ghik…®ghi, mbe th…® mavugh…®rawe vara, kaiwae gougou ma ina ghembako iyako.  
\v 26 Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye lenji vwenyevwenye bigibiginiye na lenji bigibigi ghanjiyamoyamo thovuye, ne th…® bigimenawe.  
\v 27 Ko iyemaeŇčge bigibigi raraithar…® na thanavu i monjimonjina gharavakathaŇčgi, rakwan…®Ňčgi, mane te regha i ruva e ghembako iyako t…®ne, mbe thavala eŇčge vara Loi kaerova i roriya idanji yawal…® e ghabuk t…®ne, bukuko iyako Sip Nariye le buk.   
\c 22  
\p
\v 1 Kaero nyaoma thovuye i vatomwe e ghino yawal…® mbwaniye i voruvoru, marae i woiya Ňčgoreiya galas, i voru raŇčgima Loi na Sip Nariye e lenji ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne,  
\v 2 na i voru na i reŇča e ghambako ghakamwath…® lagh…®ye ghalughawoghawo. E mbwako ghadidiye vaŇčga na vaŇčga yawal…® ghaumbwa i ndeghath…®we, iye manjala regha na regha i raurau, na theghathegha umbwara e t…®ne mbaŇčayaworo na mbaŇčaiwo i rau. Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye th…® vakaiwoŇčaŇčgiya umbwako ndamwandamwae na mbala th…® vavur…®ghegheŇčaŇčgi.  
\v 3 Ma lolo regha o bigi regha ne inanji gheko na Loi i guraŇčgi. Loi weiye Sip Nariye lenji ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye i yaku e ghembako iyako t…®ne na Loi le rakakaiwo th…® kururuwe.  
\v 4 Ne th…® thuweya ghamwae na idae ina e ghamwanji.  
\v 5 Ma tene i gouva, na kad…®ŇčeŇče manjamanjalawae na varae manjamanjalawae ma inanjiwe, kaiwae Giya Loi iye lenji manjamanjala. Na thiye ne th…® mbaro mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako.   
\s1 Jisas le mena  
\p
\v 6 Nyaoma thovuye i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúUtuutuko thiyako emunjoru na val…®kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweghath…®. Giya Loi, iye i giya Une weŇčgiya ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®, va i variya le nyao thovuye na i woraŇčgiya weŇčgiya le rakakaiwo na th…® ghareghare budakai ne mbaŇča ubotu i yomara.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Giya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! MbaŇča nasiye ya njoghama! Thavala th…® ghambugha utuutuke e bukuke iyake t…®ne, Loi i mwaewo weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Ghino Jon ya loŇčweya utuutuko thiyako na ya thuweŇčgi bigibigike thiyake. Na mbaŇča ya loŇčwe na ya thuweŇčgi, kaero ya ronja e ghegheŇčgu vuvuye nyaoko thovuye iya i vatomweko e ghino e gheghe, na ya munje ya kururuwe.  
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúThava! Ghino rakakaiwo regha, ŇčgoraŇčgwa ghen weinaŇčgiya oghagha len val…®rakakaiwo ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye iya thavala th…® ghambu ghabukuke iyake le utuutu. U kururuwe eŇčge Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Na mbowo i dageva e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi le utuutu e bukuke iyake t…®ne iya i utuŇča budakai ne th…® yomara noroke na mbaŇča i menamenako, thava u wothuwele weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, kaiwae mbaŇča kaero i ghenetha moli.  
\v 11 ThoŇčgo thela i vakavakatha thar…®, mbe th…® rombele vara thar…® ghavakatha! Thavala e yawalinjiko nuwaiya renuwaŇča raraithar…®, mbe th…® rombele vara thanavuko iyako. Na thavala th…® vakavakatha rumwaru, mbe th…® rombele vara rumwaruko ghavakatha. Na thavala th…® boboma, lenji yakuyaku mbe Ňčgoreiye vara iyako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 Giya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! MbaŇča nasiye ya njoghama. Ne ya bigimena modami, regha na regha modae ne ya giyawe tembe Ňčgoreiyeva le vakathako.  
\v 13 Ghino Alepa na Omega! Ghino ya viva na ya rereghamba. Ghino va Irikowe na ne Eleghambako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúThavala th…® thavwiya ghanjikwama molao na i kakaleva, Loi ghare weŇčgi. Thiye val…®kaiwanji th…® ghana yawal…® ghaumbwa une, na val…®kaiwanji th…® ru e ghamba ruko na th…® wa e ghembako t…®ne.  
\v 15 Ko iyemaeŇčge thavala th…® vakavakatha monjina thanavuniye, th…® kukukura, rayathiyathima, ragabo, th…® kurukururu weŇčgiya loi kwan…®kwan, na thavala th…® gharethovuŇča kwan thanavuniye na th…® vakavakatha, thiye ne thiya yaku e gana ghereiye.   
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúGhino Jisas ya variya lo nyao thovuye i ghaona i utuŇča bigibigiko thiyako e ghemi, ghemi iya hu yayaku ekelesiyana e t…®nenji. Ghino Deivid gheuu rumbuniye, na ghino th…®nambaŇča vogh…®t…®na woyaya lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Nyao Boboma weiye Sip Nariye ghaghaivaun th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU mena!‚ÄĚ  
\p Taulagh…®na ghemi iya hu loŇčweya totoke iyake huŇča, ‚ÄúU mena!‚ÄĚ  
\p Thela thoŇčgo mbwa i ghar…® na nuwaiya mbwa, i mena mbema i mun eŇčge yawal…® mbwaniye, ma e modamodae.   
\s1 Utu momouniye  
\p
\v 18 Ghino, Jisas, ya Ňčaevavair…®Ňčga, ghar…®ghar…®na wolagh…®ye ghemi hu loŇčweya Loi ghal…®Ňčae e bukuke iyake t…®ne iya i utuŇča budakai ne th…® yomara noroke na mbaŇča i menamenako. ThoŇčgo lolo regha i vatabo utuutuke iyake mbe e utuutu regha, Loi ne i lith…® weya loloko iyako, ne i vatabo ghadagaborakowe iya bukuke iyake i govambwarake e t…®nenji.  
\v 19 Na thoŇčgo lolo regha i rakayathu utuutu regha e bukuke iyake t…®ne, iya i utuŇča budakaiya ne th…® yomara noroke na mbaŇča i menamenako, Loi ne i woraŇčgiyawe iya thovuyeko bukuke iyake i woraŇčgiyaŇčgi, mane i vatomwewe i ghana yawal…® ghaumbwa une, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva mane i ru e ghemba bobomako t…®ne.   
\p
\v 20 Jisas iye i utuŇča bigibigiko thiyako utuninji, i utu Ňčgoreiyake: ‚ÄúEmunjoru, mbaŇča nasiye ya njoghama.‚ÄĚ  
\p Mbwana, Ňägoreiye! Giya Jisas, u mena!   
\p
\v 21 Giya Jisas ghare weŇčga taulagh…®na e ghemi.\fig |alt="Jesus hands upraised" src="cn01885B.tif" size="span" copy="Cook" ref="22:21" \fig*   